<h2 local-id=3D"5cd992406d81" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-UniqueValuePropositions">Unique Value Proposit=
ions</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"fce4650d-4b64-4a31-b7a1-5780d88e6f93">
<li local-id=3D"f9070838-46e3-4eaa-9c3c-3e8b95f716bb">
<p local-id=3D"ade0667f264a">Voice-First AI Interaction: Hands-free managem=
ent via natural language commands</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc667dd6-a30a-4289-a4e7-a102b2408305">
<p local-id=3D"fc7211f0b36e">Specialized AI Agents: Domain-specific intelli=
gence (Finance, Tasks, Calendar, etc.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"78b0bac7-c81f-4e7f-82a5-61610336e9e7">
<p local-id=3D"2d9c909d610f">European Privacy Standards: GDPR-compliant by =
design, data sovereignty</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"010c5638-9e41-4848-8a01-7cdaccaba9cc">
<p local-id=3D"c5f1299bd6fa">All-in-One Platform: Replace 5-7 separate apps=
 with one unified system</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e490228b-c4ee-49c3-8179-728e6dfc5ce6">
<p local-id=3D"f9f66d5203b2">Offline-First Core Features: Calendar and list=
s work without internet</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"be9d33e1-d43f-4d98-a349-06b1825459ac">
<p local-id=3D"55fb765b73de">Smart Automation: AI orchestrator learns patte=
rns and suggests optimizations</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"83cd0f364076"></p>
<p local-id=3D"ef37138b0967"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"1c5efc607d1a" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.CoreModules-FirstPrinciplesBreakdown">4. Cor=
e Modules - First Principles Breakdown</h1>
<p local-id=3D"e0f797890ecc">Each module is designed from first principles,=
 starting with the fundamental user need and deriving the minimal feature s=
et required for MVP. Features are prioritized based on frequency of use, cr=
itical user need, and technical feasibility within the 10-week timeline.</p=
>
<h2 local-id=3D"e89aef23d317" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.1Calendar&amp;Scheduling">4.1 Calendar &amp;=
 Scheduling</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"61717b28b0ac" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FirstPrincipleAnalysis">First Principle Analys=
is</h3>
<p local-id=3D"19d8c9c9b53e">Fundamental Truth: Families must coordinate "w=
hen" activities happen across multiple people with conflicting schedules. T=
ime conflicts create stress and missed obligations.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"3f0db8349b05" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CoreUserNeed">Core User Need</h3>
<p local-id=3D"dcbd7e5eb64d">Know what everyone is doing, when they are doi=
ng it, and whether there are conflicts.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"9fb2521a9dd3" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MVPFeatures(PriorityP0-MustHave)">MVP Features=
 (Priority P0 - Must Have)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"997d0b73-d600-4449-9f56-e1a527edbd59">
<li local-id=3D"51e919db-e711-4a87-a0c8-d1d79f6b8c57">
<p local-id=3D"f1e59230afc1">Shared Family Calendar View: All family events=
 visible in one calendar</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"716830bb-6401-436b-85ee-05842f6e8c2e">
<p local-id=3D"8babe2bcec1a">Event Creation: Title, date/time, location, at=
tendees, notes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db4c8401-f93b-451a-bbab-ae12b9dbad37">
<p local-id=3D"bee84ab02e4d">Event Types: Color-coded categories (work, sch=
ool, appointments, activities)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6c6e09e-28cb-4b3c-b8f6-07631528d15d">
<p local-id=3D"6364dba72ac5">Conflict Detection: Visual indicators when eve=
nts overlap for same person</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"386e1b76-41d9-4a49-a93c-50ee2568746c">
<p local-id=3D"8421ebb90200">Reminders: Time-based notifications (15 min, 1=
 hour, 1 day before)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22eed0c6-1975-427b-9f61-f0f9ccbfa7b2">
<p local-id=3D"10a7175cf556">Recurring Events: Daily, weekly, monthly patte=
rns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4f6aede-c9c1-4696-9467-0b9bacdff329">
<p local-id=3D"0ba74cdf6c0c">Multiple Views: Day, week, month, agenda list<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb1a44bc-065d-45fb-93fc-666cef5d9094">
<p local-id=3D"fca638b684e0">Offline Access: View calendar and add events w=
ithout internet</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"a99615b40b99" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceCommands(CalendarAgent)">Voice Commands (=
Calendar Agent)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"157c50f8-41be-4d29-9be2-95d06fdd2723">
<li local-id=3D"773647df-a2a7-40e0-be32-a5000e7e3f94">
<p local-id=3D"d96eaf090009">"Add dentist appointment next Tuesday at 3pm"<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a915dc1d-7259-4bd9-9542-696d908d3723">
<p local-id=3D"bcc359064c2a">"What do I have tomorrow?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1be29535-819a-4c7a-82fc-9317e1c4d904">
<p local-id=3D"401109234dc3">"When is Sarah's soccer practice?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"41931c7b-d835-439a-b3b3-d9dcfbc827b2">
<p local-id=3D"3c353081ea9c">"Move my 2pm meeting to Thursday"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"27f21d08-a44d-4a04-94bb-32e0da741e47">
<p local-id=3D"ad1934572239">"Do we have any conflicts this week?"</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5f7a91dd764c" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AutomaticUpdates&amp;Notifications">Automatic =
Updates &amp; Notifications</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d5a74a2a-d6e0-45da-9d14-c343f1f642d0">
<li local-id=3D"baf27abf-6310-44ad-a3d2-366f3d300e85">
<p local-id=3D"b3d15a9f8083">Push notification 15 minutes before events</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"2a27d6a2-0334-4db4-a09c-fbd9e27fa65b">
<p local-id=3D"870226369b4b">Daily morning summary of today's schedule</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"d2a76be5-c23c-437f-af31-c90153cf0603">
<p local-id=3D"2622a407b9ad">Weekly preview every Sunday evening</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e6ff144-09ea-4e43-ba79-1f5975cbf3cd">
<p local-id=3D"3d33e1842ce1">Conflict alerts when overlapping events are cr=
eated</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8dac0574c352" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataModel(FirstPrinciples)">Data Model (First =
Principles)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"6ff144007239">Event Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"d5a7b380-af87-4508-8b1f-17c051d3f0c4">
<li local-id=3D"9db40523-c2be-4fd3-9c40-c34916272b02">
<p local-id=3D"864ff08abb61">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1cdef786-92d3-4b82-8e31-47abc79d6eff">
<p local-id=3D"65c37e90c94b">title (what)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13deaf8c-4687-43e7-9e13-daa43eb24fed">
<p local-id=3D"97b87fde5a9d">start_time, end_time (when)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"34344df8-6f37-4370-940e-ca79a9c5b681">
<p local-id=3D"870b89b6e1dc">location (where)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a41b0f81-166b-40e1-96bc-57462b5ecb41">
<p local-id=3D"42decd1a31d6">attendees (who - family member IDs)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e5bb33e-6ea4-40a2-96ba-d6e310aebb0b">
<p local-id=3D"731cc38ed4df">category (event type)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"928ed91f-3afa-4493-931e-15e9d8474853">
<p local-id=3D"bf185d92ffaf">recurrence_pattern (if recurring)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3b0e1c5-a67b-45ca-8e83-a95c183d1365">
<p local-id=3D"6cfe8c6f88fd">reminder_settings (notification preferences)</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b06dd77-df40-41bf-a041-2cc87973da4b">
<p local-id=3D"0f0a656bb561">notes (additional context)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"abc893278ade" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DeferredtoPost-MVP">Deferred to Post-MVP</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"08474b7a-ec98-406c-b978-9bfc2a669d2d">
<li local-id=3D"f6d65a6c-6530-4a64-acf0-6a2d5a000f37">
<p local-id=3D"e0b02cee39d7">External calendar sync (Google Calendar, Apple=
 Calendar)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a81ca63b-5038-4b50-a2af-a07d0f71efd8">
<p local-id=3D"3a680160a453">Location-based reminders (geo-fencing)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"15d96213-ab0d-45f3-8b9f-8b8f9422ea18">
<p local-id=3D"e7b1239ab0aa">Travel time calculation and notifications</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"dce9242f-f144-48c9-9fb7-1499af024c83">
<p local-id=3D"739b2a30a257">Availability checking and scheduling assistant=
</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"a6b33df5947f"></p>
<p local-id=3D"ae4ba863e8d5"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"797295700557" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.2Tasks&amp;Chores">4.2 Tasks &amp; Chores</h=
2>
<h3 local-id=3D"4397594a7200" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FirstPrincipleAnalysis.1">First Principle Anal=
ysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c95fd53a980e">Fundamental Truth: Families have responsibilit=
ies that must be distributed, tracked, and completed. Unequal distribution =
creates resentment; incomplete tasks create dysfunction.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"3d3ea04ab8b6" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CoreUserNeed.1">Core User Need</h3>
<p local-id=3D"9ae4da37a387">Fair distribution of household work with visib=
ility into who is doing what and accountability for completion.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"b24b7cf32bc1" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MVPFeatures(PriorityP0-MustHave).1">MVP Featur=
es (Priority P0 - Must Have)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"5431b448-e6f2-4b13-9f49-73e37fc7b6f1">
<li local-id=3D"ee17dd98-3128-415b-9122-296a23ab0acd">
<p local-id=3D"740d3a3f43a3">Task Creation: Title, description, due date, p=
riority level</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"875b15bb-0528-4934-8a93-980dada8fdae">
<p local-id=3D"4687bb0cbff0">Assignment: Assign to specific family member(s=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f543011d-f142-4b01-8ca3-e9de833cb075">
<p local-id=3D"dcb549a85344">Status Tracking: Not Started, In Progress, Com=
pleted</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"981df04d-77f7-4eeb-9444-bed1c2977e52">
<p local-id=3D"a99cf7b53070">Recurring Tasks: Daily, weekly, monthly chores=
 (e.g., "Take out trash every Tuesday")</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"05bd61f6-5bf1-490a-a18d-46a10d9bc93d">
<p local-id=3D"b976b51d8aed">Priority Levels: Low, Medium, High, Urgent</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"fe5d7f89-5f4d-4fa6-a901-f22bc811bd74">
<p local-id=3D"9522a5454c81">Due Date Reminders: Notifications 1 day before=
 and on due date</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"638d5315-1e41-4f9f-bfb0-1cf18e0a3490">
<p local-id=3D"906ec40de215">Completion Tracking: Mark complete, view histo=
ry</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c0b8f23e-af17-400e-b3e2-c3ca3d6970e8">
<p local-id=3D"ecc2c2eb030e">Family Dashboard: Overview of all tasks, filte=
red by person or status</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"3f7beb32e34b" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceCommands(TaskAgent)">Voice Commands (Task=
 Agent)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ef5a415d-258c-434d-837d-28ddd089c206">
<li local-id=3D"da5fe025-c795-40fe-9ff9-f4424bfc19e6">
<p local-id=3D"1acd6c60accc">"Add task: Buy birthday gift for Mom, due this=
 Friday"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f1ceefb0-ab5e-45b4-8f89-18104dddc61d">
<p local-id=3D"967030b48d50">"Assign laundry to Sarah"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bcb10ec0-901e-454e-a9be-00a501f5c07f">
<p local-id=3D"6278fbeceac5">"What tasks do I have today?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c85daf2c-5c12-4528-a887-3d9a50746d0f">
<p local-id=3D"7f0694ce2cd6">"Mark grocery shopping as complete"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3f5829b2-7ee9-41a7-8486-873558d8f00a">
<p local-id=3D"4881385ea84f">"Show me all overdue tasks"</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"97d545e42836" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AutomaticUpdates&amp;Notifications.1">Automati=
c Updates &amp; Notifications</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"8f612ddc-1589-4db9-b1c8-d9805a8afb57">
<li local-id=3D"b50e1d90-a9b9-4ce3-b0f0-e7a9d5983e82">
<p local-id=3D"6316b32bcfce">Daily morning task summary for each family mem=
ber</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"db2adf46-1343-411f-b4e5-bf8aef48175d">
<p local-id=3D"5d6f7efc5388">Due date reminders (1 day before, day of)</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"d9285f8a-3dfb-415c-9b03-b726665e6280">
<p local-id=3D"081ff7a7dbaf">Overdue task alerts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"17f82714-3eb3-45fd-a038-68c96ec4b08a">
<p local-id=3D"c473bf49cb65">Completion notifications to task creator</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"1ffae932-0713-4b48-8cec-becec69582b5">
<p local-id=3D"b847be7ecb97">Weekly family task summary (workload distribut=
ion)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"857239ad371b" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataModel(FirstPrinciples).1">Data Model (Firs=
t Principles)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e4985a796946">Task Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"bd218ba5-380b-41c3-9a24-67c76e77bee8">
<li local-id=3D"157ea312-a904-4d5c-87f1-199b8fd03cbf">
<p local-id=3D"624e739cceb8">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3c7c2fcd-bf13-45b2-a14c-f8294c6fe097">
<p local-id=3D"f91de64ddadf">title (what needs to be done)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1032d498-28cc-48bf-9ef5-40a0cd55ab61">
<p local-id=3D"4f412985d5b7">description (detailed instructions)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0cf1a34-4371-4b30-9023-a7bdcd7e7447">
<p local-id=3D"797a902a74a1">assigned_to (family member ID)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"66feae0b-cc21-47b2-a44c-b09153254f3f">
<p local-id=3D"f7b376a28fcc">created_by (family member ID)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"98678aba-95e1-4204-b1fd-c2a0752bf42f">
<p local-id=3D"6c445d99e087">due_date (deadline)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a879b284-56ef-4814-beae-b6a900fb6d05">
<p local-id=3D"1b9bd7db1223">priority (urgency level)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"05a9b8f0-9ffe-49ae-aecd-ad8e24c13751">
<p local-id=3D"d8fa87ef2871">status (lifecycle state)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"be7d9435-4524-4685-8f93-080388f7804a">
<p local-id=3D"a6d0b64bf0dc">recurrence_pattern (if recurring)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58a7e7bb-1eb7-45ba-8ae8-ab231781a07f">
<p local-id=3D"6e57f7de9b7d">completed_at (timestamp)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6ebaad01a521" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-KeyMetricstoTrack">Key Metrics to Track</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"449d3c4a-b062-4bb7-9089-dd74c0e3d47f">
<li local-id=3D"b335b27c-8f29-4a6e-9353-730a0e988cb9">
<p local-id=3D"f05cddab595c">Task completion rate per family member</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"4839b028-29f7-4506-b46d-c7dcc6151b72">
<p local-id=3D"5bc46607b4ca">Average time to completion</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbb6ba3a-2086-426a-a963-e12f2dbd7e44">
<p local-id=3D"2f5e65d881ac">Workload distribution (are tasks fairly distri=
buted?)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c90f805-6015-468c-a53e-bdada5efa34a">
<p local-id=3D"312f78ce2aef">Overdue task rate</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"988e9faa1817" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DeferredtoPost-MVP.1">Deferred to Post-MVP</h3=
>
<ul local-id=3D"278838cf-b9d5-4f40-8ab7-031819be6fec">
<li local-id=3D"c8696e36-f5f7-45ae-a7e9-82a484985aa9">
<p local-id=3D"76c4e6ca3b1c">Subtasks and task dependencies</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ffc2b98-e99c-49c6-a4e4-39a254f323f2">
<p local-id=3D"54743f6109f3">Chore rotation automation (auto-assign based o=
n fairness algorithm)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fd081c4d-98f0-4549-9e18-c2b9958829a7">
<p local-id=3D"facbe285592c">Points/gamification for children</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a61818f1-a47a-4c28-8fa0-5e1ac62e6002">
<p local-id=3D"faa9813de6a5">Task templates and quick-add common chores</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"233809555af1"></p>
<p local-id=3D"ea32ee8d8347"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"edfa4529bf90" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.3SharedLists">4.3 Shared Lists</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"665877b436e5" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FirstPrincipleAnalysis.2">First Principle Anal=
ysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e75cdadc9773">Fundamental Truth: Families need to coordinate=
 on shared resources and purchases. Without shared lists, there is duplicat=
ion (buying same item twice) or omission (forgetting needed items).</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"66ce67bbb8fb" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CoreUserNeed.2">Core User Need</h3>
<p local-id=3D"2e7c6a359caf">Real-time synchronized lists that all family m=
embers can view and edit to prevent duplication and ensure completeness.</p=
>
<h3 local-id=3D"6bc6bc2e2cc8" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MVPFeatures(PriorityP0-MustHave).2">MVP Featur=
es (Priority P0 - Must Have)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"95ac0bd4-831a-43a9-956e-e5b27d79225c">
<li local-id=3D"ae5af17d-5be4-45e0-a564-4697d5dd6385">
<p local-id=3D"930b6bcd0a2a">Multiple Lists: Create unlimited lists (Grocer=
ies, Shopping, To-Buy, Packing, etc.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c8b681ba-b2dc-479d-bee7-1df901715bba">
<p local-id=3D"fcf41ca288a5">Add/Remove Items: Simple text input with insta=
nt sync</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f163e66f-eb0e-4a6f-a573-ff531ef20620">
<p local-id=3D"052be9a62ac3">Check Off Items: Mark items as completed/purch=
ased</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d13b8c93-e11c-444d-a2e0-3ab6b3a5fe53">
<p local-id=3D"4c260eb3e972">Real-Time Sync: Changes appear immediately for=
 all family members</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"931f3975-3706-42df-b511-0b9ddf53ee81">
<p local-id=3D"bf631603b22a">List Templates: Pre-made templates (Weekly Gro=
ceries, Vacation Packing)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c87f6557-e609-466a-a260-c825e36c1f30">
<p local-id=3D"f1791ee8f507">Quantity/Notes: Add quantity and notes to item=
s</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8612a141-300e-4f2e-ab04-a65f5ae2ce92">
<p local-id=3D"353149533fe5">Offline Access: View and edit lists offline, s=
ync when online</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5e6b0dad-66c9-4780-a494-087c2d0ffd34">
<p local-id=3D"59d1c39cac1d">Archive Completed Items: Hide but preserve pur=
chase history</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"44faeb5de56d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceCommands(ListAgent)">Voice Commands (List=
 Agent)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d46a8450-9768-48ae-8df7-7e388e39c1d7">
<li local-id=3D"6ed681f8-b192-4a57-88e2-1ae7c0cac000">
<p local-id=3D"2fe3b9aa383b">"Add milk to grocery list"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"df7663df-9e09-469f-b977-4db9fdaefc99">
<p local-id=3D"15165fb42a96">"Show me the grocery list"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c984b481-5f0c-419d-bf34-29841b480289">
<p local-id=3D"e82e0ccd41be">"Check off bread"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"76451a07-126b-4e2c-80fb-76f4a3551b39">
<p local-id=3D"3245aea9aee0">"Create a new list called vacation packing"</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbb2d1e2-a162-498a-bf16-9fe373a46fb6">
<p local-id=3D"065629e9a74f">"What's left on the shopping list?"</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"b7e76e601b56" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AutomaticUpdates&amp;Notifications.2">Automati=
c Updates &amp; Notifications</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"dc556d74-966c-463d-9ac7-8d1dc6754cff">
<li local-id=3D"9812d7f7-b140-4628-9324-4a742f662344">
<p local-id=3D"aadb0093b028">Real-time sync: Changes pushed instantly to al=
l devices</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5a4e6e49-0d0f-45e4-a280-bdaab0a3ca31">
<p local-id=3D"33f23a6d356d">Notification when someone adds items (optional=
 setting)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5c1c4734-ad48-406e-a941-559dfbacc0c7">
<p local-id=3D"8c8d702778ed">Notification when someone completes shopping t=
rip (all items checked)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d6ed0e5d7958" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataModel(FirstPrinciples).2">Data Model (Firs=
t Principles)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a93754037996">List Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"fe335795-7348-45ce-ae54-c7fc1db8b421">
<li local-id=3D"bec0861f-2940-45c6-b2e4-1e707e009d1a">
<p local-id=3D"1027af82fb60">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f5f0c4d-c3cb-4d86-912f-b238cb2f25e1">
<p local-id=3D"86ffd4c4c1ff">name (list title)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c0a76e3-a32f-499c-b767-6d7c279be060">
<p local-id=3D"c66027b5f506">type (category: grocery, shopping, packing, et=
c.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aed2b2b4-e0b5-48a4-a322-2f356bd0ddb5">
<p local-id=3D"dca59ceb3d92">created_by (family member ID)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3737c433-09e5-4bf2-9c3c-c580f8f77eda">
<p local-id=3D"85f11808847e">items[] (array of list items)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f0d8c076a1fd">List Item Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"277bb471-2a17-4255-8d46-a9a83c60f87e">
<li local-id=3D"765190d0-f545-4ebb-b1fa-951901d7388d">
<p local-id=3D"4f2e7659d8d0">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13eb9c28-dbee-47b4-a4ef-51aa74555cec">
<p local-id=3D"c99d794f0013">text (item name)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f0508737-a8fb-4c70-b95f-0d7e887b4235">
<p local-id=3D"3dd8fb006015">quantity (amount needed)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bc2b60e-485b-4e47-945a-2c8017ea51f9">
<p local-id=3D"d81ec6af4b3a">notes (additional details)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef2703f6-0f1e-4138-8001-1c7bd1adaca1">
<p local-id=3D"3f53c87dc65f">is_completed (checked off status)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"655c0e46-62a0-4877-b984-fd64f57bb1bb">
<p local-id=3D"2710e3d6ba8e">added_by (family member ID)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d30e7878-f49b-43f8-9fce-d1cd82316eea">
<p local-id=3D"43b70d6dba3b">completed_by (who checked it off)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"016760a8ecb5" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DeferredtoPost-MVP.2">Deferred to Post-MVP</h3=
>
<ul local-id=3D"0c5e8879-651b-4a14-b45d-280f08d47d49">
<li local-id=3D"f17a3d4f-2d1c-4ce9-9f13-1ea1430988ac">
<p local-id=3D"8e982f040f06">Smart categorization (auto-organize grocery li=
st by aisle)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b84fe6e9-79fc-4194-9d07-1b855b94a8af">
<p local-id=3D"5df0cbbd641b">Price tracking and budget estimates</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6137e73-7847-46bb-a1fa-7de9019fcd1b">
<p local-id=3D"59fee9ef8400">Barcode scanning to add items</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e78593a5-3fe0-4300-b1ea-3efa7be5e391">
<p local-id=3D"03025f7d1506">Recurring list items (auto-add milk every week=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00cde152-348e-4d5b-a796-8aca729398b9">
<p local-id=3D"34e363449b7c">Integration with grocery delivery services</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"110effd9c340"></p>
<p local-id=3D"e96b8ca09fa8"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"46e4af92279c" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.4ExpenseTracking">4.4 Expense Tracking</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"d74e1085cad0" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FirstPrincipleAnalysis.3">First Principle Anal=
ysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"2ed269d8866c">Fundamental Truth: Families share financial re=
sources that flow in (income) and out (expenses). Without visibility, overs=
pending occurs and financial stress increases.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"a7044c1ef041" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CoreUserNeed.3">Core User Need</h3>
<p local-id=3D"6ced8dadecf8">Shared visibility into where money is going, w=
ith simple budget tracking and category-based analysis to prevent overspend=
ing.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"343612ae014d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MVPFeatures(PriorityP0-MustHave).3">MVP Featur=
es (Priority P0 - Must Have)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f509e278-dd11-491e-ab5d-bfa99a7db5dd">
<li local-id=3D"7bb0f8e4-9386-4b2b-8570-b2dfd2006ff5">
<p local-id=3D"f759c907b373">Manual Expense Entry: Amount, category, date, =
description, who paid</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dc42fc21-d02d-432b-85fa-a13d2f835c37">
<p local-id=3D"702faf68f317">Expense Categories: Pre-defined categories (Gr=
oceries, Dining, Utilities, Transport, etc.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef9f31a2-a944-4214-9539-632584f2c3df">
<p local-id=3D"17b8b757a106">Receipt Photo Capture: Take photo of receipt a=
nd attach to expense</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e246cd60-5313-488d-bd03-be058c476c7e">
<p local-id=3D"aaf27dd6f914">Monthly Budget Setting: Set budget limits per =
category</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff69e06c-79b5-4f8e-828a-d6c2ec6feed3">
<p local-id=3D"1b0299a19397">Budget Alerts: Notifications when approaching =
or exceeding budget (80%, 100%)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6dd158cf-d29f-4484-86ef-955787ace3e1">
<p local-id=3D"e384ece36b4b">Spending Summary: View total spent by category=
, week, month</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"47baabca-6db9-4e81-820d-aa5e19b6c675">
<p local-id=3D"7aa0379c96cd">Shared Expenses: Tag expenses as shared or ind=
ividual</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ed35813f-a841-4cf3-b1ba-5d2b3c2187b5">
<p local-id=3D"fc7f8d656346">Simple Charts: Pie chart of spending by catego=
ry, line graph over time</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"4a0fb659876c" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceCommands(FinanceAgent)">Voice Commands (F=
inance Agent)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"b74b4119-a564-4ee7-8db5-65cd1f4bf55c">
<li local-id=3D"ac1d5128-bf23-4227-9eb7-673ef16b4425">
<p local-id=3D"d0136d5fb71c">"Add expense: 45 euros for groceries at Carref=
our"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d815cd93-e11a-4ad9-afca-711ef286b453">
<p local-id=3D"f6ebef8274a5">"How much have we spent on dining this month?"=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3cba8f1-b8ce-48a6-bf48-d2f91cd18ef8">
<p local-id=3D"9a6ab9258d30">"Show me our grocery budget status"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3cef69a1-f62a-4b68-adc3-0f070feefe1a">
<p local-id=3D"753cea199152">"What did we spend this week?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d468136-81f6-46a2-81db-183811fed60c">
<p local-id=3D"26d9c92c029e">"Are we over budget on anything?"</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d2a467878268" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AutomaticUpdates&amp;Notifications.3">Automati=
c Updates &amp; Notifications</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"a341209e-7b4b-4b68-9a5f-d51f6f9942c3">
<li local-id=3D"f9bcd1d7-0c15-404a-98b2-8708255e8352">
<p local-id=3D"de8138ef64bf">Monthly spending summary at end of each month<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"026d603b-b8a6-4911-95d2-cf680afec42a">
<p local-id=3D"b42a185d485c">Budget alerts at 80% and 100% thresholds</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"0f59cb30-dead-45b4-8c72-bf23e2dfda8c">
<p local-id=3D"4050fa555a79">Weekly spending recap every Sunday</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e492169-b917-4492-8311-0fb835a65c4f">
<p local-id=3D"79e7234608e1">Unusual spending pattern alerts (optional, AI-=
powered)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"90a7d85acf8d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataModel(FirstPrinciples).3">Data Model (Firs=
t Principles)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8e2c599a4597">Expense Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"802950d9-0126-4175-a6bd-b23aa635e3f7">
<li local-id=3D"06066db2-d953-4b64-b2cc-43064af023a5">
<p local-id=3D"79df03d3a185">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"27d4df69-7f9c-4c0b-ab31-3d79715791bb">
<p local-id=3D"952623073033">amount (money spent)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aee42f3a-aea3-41c1-a094-ef813516ba43">
<p local-id=3D"cf26dc1679a4">currency (EUR, USD, etc.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"26293eef-6228-465e-a1f7-902ddf14b8a7">
<p local-id=3D"6e503c73e7f9">category (expense type)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"022df663-10f1-4735-b0b9-7160c988cc79">
<p local-id=3D"3a86dad62891">date (when expense occurred)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bb6aa86-c1e2-43d6-b6a0-f6861d51aa4b">
<p local-id=3D"04e65b116a6e">description (what was purchased)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc0fd7d3-83d1-4ab8-a62a-3211ea0b37eb">
<p local-id=3D"8955749907a8">paid_by (family member ID)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9fe6142e-7b2b-4fe8-a352-c4917d181532">
<p local-id=3D"544d04fa24e6">is_shared (boolean)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e1b41fc0-4d9b-4517-8404-9834d7711a57">
<p local-id=3D"4eb302b684d1">receipt_image_url (optional photo)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b108f206-0045-47ea-9910-3fd433dafad4">
<p local-id=3D"68bbf42e9b2a">merchant_name (where purchased)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"95d0880a546b">Budget Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0151ad44-501b-40b8-a173-003a7490663c">
<li local-id=3D"80ee7ec7-b255-4f71-b4ed-28a75e6bdefd">
<p local-id=3D"247d29bea90f">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"da3e5935-92fd-4f04-80a6-8572b8bcc9a4">
<p local-id=3D"f731bdc5f605">category (budget category)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67bb16b7-a5ff-494b-944d-b8caee0352f1">
<p local-id=3D"95329d8eddfa">monthly_limit (budget amount)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"32f6f162-9b56-4492-8b7d-4d116ba52bab">
<p local-id=3D"094935553d67">currency (EUR, USD, etc.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"537173f7-ee0a-4bf4-9a32-239f5dc86751">
<p local-id=3D"8175e959dffb">alert_threshold (percentage for notification)<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d6ee1fb686df" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AIFinanceAgentCapabilities(Premium)">AI Financ=
e Agent Capabilities (Premium)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ca070a8b-4112-4fae-ab6e-4d0b442ec5cc">
<li local-id=3D"655ad677-05a0-4af1-91e7-4d8d038cedd8">
<p local-id=3D"143f5634b9b7">Budget optimization suggestions based on spend=
ing patterns</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81f66a54-d43e-4b75-bbf7-c180cbf98240">
<p local-id=3D"204b5cd60e3b">Anomaly detection (unusual purchases)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d1a26149-4d64-4947-8ed6-e7fdcef8e9cf">
<p local-id=3D"dc26edd2860c">Spending insights and trends analysis</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c38338f-2c01-40aa-9eed-529539cdd450">
<p local-id=3D"8485b6be80d4">Category recommendations based on description<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"f1952cdfab12" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DeferredtoPost-MVP.3">Deferred to Post-MVP</h3=
>
<ul local-id=3D"06880dae-6bf3-4a2d-b234-c6f30b087282">
<li local-id=3D"b478556c-09b5-4220-8090-f521bbc6d773">
<p local-id=3D"dd1191d2f887">Bank account integration and automatic transac=
tion import</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3cc64b66-304f-48e7-82de-b96a622c8cc4">
<p local-id=3D"5977738bc8c4">Bill payment tracking and reminders</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a7745154-4c6c-4e02-938f-653ee07c8ef9">
<p local-id=3D"f445e8991c4a">Income tracking</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4fb7b742-ff2a-49f0-9523-b7e3b38956a5">
<p local-id=3D"de5f5c88946e">Debt/loan tracking</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2aa8241-a2f1-4efd-90a7-a2e8ae6fe4ce">
<p local-id=3D"0d8582e680a1">Financial goal setting (save for vacation, etc=
.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bb456544-af4a-417e-87eb-6fb2ea7a72e0">
<p local-id=3D"c43acd6a3105">Split expense calculations and settlement</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c2fff8e117c0"></p>
