<h2 local-id=3D"7ad80af76fbc" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.5FamilyFeed">4.5 Family Feed</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"cd5caa9ae981" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FirstPrincipleAnalysis.4">First Principle Anal=
ysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a87b80f3567c">Fundamental Truth: Family members need to shar=
e updates, photos, and information asynchronously. Not everything requires =
real-time chat; some communication is informational and can be consumed whe=
n convenient.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"2480c9789594" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CoreUserNeed.4">Core User Need</h3>
<p local-id=3D"553bea15bc47">A private family space to share updates, photo=
s, announcements, and everyday moments without the noise and privacy concer=
ns of social media.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"e55ba53eb370" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MVPFeatures(PriorityP0-MustHave).4">MVP Featur=
es (Priority P0 - Must Have)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"56946de7-57bc-4855-b988-7fe1425f86a0">
<li local-id=3D"1ec7f2e9-88ba-43ee-9ead-4217990ef812">
<p local-id=3D"7269b3a8a1c1">Post Updates: Text, photos, or both</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"90b529df-291e-4a3d-bd42-c6a24f83947a">
<p local-id=3D"5d379aaacc56">Comments: Family members can comment on posts<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13dd56e6-e573-4480-9891-75b9aaa26787">
<p local-id=3D"6b46cc457371">Reactions: Simple emoji reactions (=E2=9D=A4=
=EF=B8=8F, =F0=9F=91=8D, =F0=9F=98=82)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"36e181b0-dc1d-4277-aeab-0ab7743d9af1">
<p local-id=3D"fdec6899b9ad">Chronological Feed: Time-ordered posts, newest=
 first</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03604ecc-1c2a-4306-806f-164d674e180a">
<p local-id=3D"1f1f7b1fd060">Photo Uploads: Multiple photos per post</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"e9338a38-057b-4368-a11f-85fb1bfa0748">
<p local-id=3D"4094ce569195">Notifications: Alert when someone posts or com=
ments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22dcebf8-fa3a-4f13-aa76-529217cfd135">
<p local-id=3D"bfd96f1f3436">Post Types: General update, announcement, ques=
tion, photo album</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2706502b-ef75-4e5b-820d-0f695292b369">
<p local-id=3D"004d8fd5fcaf">Delete/Edit: Authors can edit or delete their =
own posts</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"07eeb0768451" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceCommands(FeedAgent)">Voice Commands (Feed=
 Agent)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"afe9abe5-3fd4-4265-934d-18f650d50217">
<li local-id=3D"222bb7b2-e777-4a6b-8d54-904af752ff82">
<p local-id=3D"9d3b59cfc1a9">"Post to family feed: Had a great day at the p=
ark"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cbe8239-8730-4214-877a-7408d31856aa">
<p local-id=3D"f05834cd9915">"Show me latest family feed posts"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a17f5261-6688-4c22-814d-126658bf6361">
<p local-id=3D"3a55900343de">"Comment on Mom's post: That looks delicious"<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"9ca809a3a816" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AutomaticUpdates&amp;Notifications.4">Automati=
c Updates &amp; Notifications</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"555f889f-5511-4167-8037-687292f8c398">
<li local-id=3D"5cbe5cc6-fde7-4c80-844d-846ea6515090">
<p local-id=3D"102b2863132c">Push notification when someone posts (can be t=
urned off)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"49eed78b-d218-4c17-89ed-a48f4ae42978">
<p local-id=3D"6dab7fe9570b">Notification when someone comments on your pos=
t</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03349a95-4b39-4c0d-888a-649bfc700491">
<p local-id=3D"78caaf13a507">Daily digest option (one summary notification =
per day)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6e7a5824966e" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataModel(FirstPrinciples).4">Data Model (Firs=
t Principles)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"43e47466bac0">Post Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"1c8c0031-4254-45cc-a3c1-e3ad82337641">
<li local-id=3D"8e79ace3-e7df-41c7-adaf-1e43aa2bbf67">
<p local-id=3D"afdb89ca5812">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ade9803f-a9bb-40ad-9ab8-50364bfbd52b">
<p local-id=3D"967327cd44ee">author_id (who posted)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d67d313-32ed-4dbe-9e98-535cdccee9fb">
<p local-id=3D"53bc58fd11b4">content (text of post)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f1ce576-af6d-4698-ad6a-ab0e32e57b80">
<p local-id=3D"d264dd95e920">images[] (array of image URLs)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"adf8ed27-72c6-4d2e-9c44-105060928cc9">
<p local-id=3D"491e34adc0dc">post_type (update, announcement, question, alb=
um)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"62fe4b89-33a7-4e3f-877f-d8977908e4f1">
<p local-id=3D"e83887ca2a4f">created_at (timestamp)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ee9a67a-50e1-469b-a345-4dbb6bde0999">
<p local-id=3D"83b9a382947a">edited_at (if edited)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3ee5de93-9978-4544-ab95-65875745924f">
<p local-id=3D"aa725c4765f3">reactions[] (array of reaction objects)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"801a2b2f-dc77-43bd-b2d3-112b15a94919">
<p local-id=3D"b1ba703daf71">comments[] (array of comment objects)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"eebb60d7b532">Comment Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"37afe4d6-6c03-44b2-a129-eddca07b499c">
<li local-id=3D"a1b7b389-62d2-4eb2-b550-84f057583a20">
<p local-id=3D"4ddaf016aefd">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"898574b6-c791-405d-a124-ada17c2c4cc2">
<p local-id=3D"d122a4b775fb">post_id (which post)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"051f0c15-faec-4685-bc68-d4309e1f3bba">
<p local-id=3D"d2eb516cebfb">author_id (who commented)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1cb7f979-4961-4c87-b330-001d0efb9f98">
<p local-id=3D"3700a1f337a3">content (comment text)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f857e505-be0f-4751-963b-be6e6d27da51">
<p local-id=3D"e945a36cc240">created_at (timestamp)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"418303295422" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DeferredtoPost-MVP.4">Deferred to Post-MVP</h3=
>
<ul local-id=3D"9bf15736-2731-4296-8da3-df707ebc7b8c">
<li local-id=3D"2fa55f5c-3968-4eb7-ae84-449e270ea67c">
<p local-id=3D"b14cd18e6da8">Video uploads and playback</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfe54106-40e6-4fe2-9204-76a68287f793">
<p local-id=3D"04c19c4dc1bf">Polls and questions with voting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c4311d5-0ece-4470-9643-8cb419f66253">
<p local-id=3D"181c6327e5e0">Post pinning (keep important posts at top)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"81716484-57d2-4896-852e-a9eb07cdf5d6">
<p local-id=3D"e294ffa92640">Post search and filtering</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0e5c344c-10ac-4706-b63d-c9927c19df73">
<p local-id=3D"ce9db2c072e7">Memory/timeline features (year in review)</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5b55808dced2"></p>
<p local-id=3D"164f1b4546d6"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"d1b57dec1e8e" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.6DocumentVault">4.6 Document Vault</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"6e1b0e59d8ca" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FirstPrincipleAnalysis.5">First Principle Anal=
ysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"4e07d32c3ebf">Fundamental Truth: Families accumulate importa=
nt documents (medical records, insurance policies, school papers, tax docum=
ents) that must be stored securely, organized, and easily retrieved when ne=
eded.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"23500ae98097" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CoreUserNeed.5">Core User Need</h3>
<p local-id=3D"cabce0e4f074">Secure, centralized storage for important fami=
ly documents with quick search and categorization to find documents when ur=
gently needed.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"bfbf4ede6d2e" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MVPFeatures(PriorityP0-MustHave).5">MVP Featur=
es (Priority P0 - Must Have)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f5e34939-976f-4edc-aeae-640826d1a5d5">
<li local-id=3D"580e87ec-857f-4f9a-a544-a8d878616b4f">
<p local-id=3D"caff2e5633d6">File Upload: Support PDF, images (JPG/PNG), Of=
fice docs (docx, xlsx)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c1958a57-f82e-4edf-ad28-afe7d4f0ed34">
<p local-id=3D"1359b028660c">Categorization: Pre-defined folders (Medical, =
Insurance, School, Tax, Legal, Other)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d881c68f-fcfb-4028-97b4-1d52e40c8e53">
<p local-id=3D"8d8b77335898">File Naming: Descriptive titles with metadata =
(date, type)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3f902e97-21dd-4eb6-85a4-4f8b6eb18abf">
<p local-id=3D"8c68ce4cb6fd">Search: Search by filename, category, date upl=
oaded</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1b9ddef3-45a7-47d8-85c1-e8fef2cdb7dc">
<p local-id=3D"9a21db5f91dd">Preview: In-app preview of PDFs and images</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"4c9459c1-f45f-493f-b44a-73b71fcd7a6e">
<p local-id=3D"7a04cc13632e">Download: Download files to device</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e3c3341-0985-4df1-98df-d9979797443a">
<p local-id=3D"a8b4d19bfa5c">Access Control: Parents can control which docu=
ments children can access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58c7bfbb-5a9b-428b-a3d8-cb0f5c710f0d">
<p local-id=3D"5afa0a5d908b">Encryption: All documents encrypted at rest an=
d in transit</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"c10acf9d5474" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceCommands(DocumentAgent)">Voice Commands (=
Document Agent)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"26fda5d4-bb9c-4d45-865b-b917b501cc56">
<li local-id=3D"c3b7f208-c704-4495-9ec2-6716c3a28bf9">
<p local-id=3D"bb08a9d42c44">"Upload this document to medical folder"</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"0a44c4b8-f55a-4c81-a4fc-edecc0d548e6">
<p local-id=3D"7318b1cdaaf8">"Find insurance documents"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf8c445c-f87c-45ca-8d27-f1d550b5b9b6">
<p local-id=3D"b4b1ab02a087">"Show me tax documents from 2024"</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"60b3fa9e50c3" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AutomaticUpdates&amp;Notifications.5">Automati=
c Updates &amp; Notifications</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"7c02165c-846f-4a40-8c5c-93fecda6eccb">
<li local-id=3D"0fa49a7b-6372-429b-8d8e-e82525b8c8a0">
<p local-id=3D"b3967a478266">Notification when someone uploads a document</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b07c80ec-8f10-4f66-a3c7-9527ede65e88">
<p local-id=3D"ace2a23d095c">Reminders for document expiration (if expirati=
on date set)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"c6d6fc2f4b15" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataModel(FirstPrinciples).5">Data Model (Firs=
t Principles)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ddf668f6aef4">Document Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ceac31af-c599-4f37-9660-1a1c6487dc8c">
<li local-id=3D"204beb30-524b-44bc-a189-d1f8a6ea1274">
<p local-id=3D"f620f3214548">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"09f2d427-0dee-4309-a4f8-600b69c28244">
<p local-id=3D"4bb72401432c">title (document name)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"179f3dfb-726b-4868-b786-25d5fc4489a8">
<p local-id=3D"65fddf92f759">file_url (cloud storage URL)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f351de35-5768-4dcf-9ace-d51d11e3071f">
<p local-id=3D"f203d2fe8e56">file_type (pdf, jpg, docx, etc.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2cb0d941-6dc3-4595-aff2-bc05b6c29d32">
<p local-id=3D"85eeef6a64a1">file_size (bytes)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6bde20b7-4376-420b-bbcf-125d1305d5f8">
<p local-id=3D"5f096bab556c">category (folder/category)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d658b31b-d39d-4d7a-92d3-5f656591a7a6">
<p local-id=3D"55c3541353ae">uploaded_by (family member ID)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21726d86-02d8-46f2-b5a7-22853fcc034c">
<p local-id=3D"1215867163ea">upload_date (timestamp)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"727fa108-2e3b-4237-aa0a-894822308378">
<p local-id=3D"d497c76605cf">tags[] (searchable tags)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"32298f1d-950d-40af-a960-99d86a79a786">
<p local-id=3D"5ebadea44f25">expiration_date (optional, for time-sensitive =
docs)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f9864da-675b-410c-be11-2ad8858d00e0">
<p local-id=3D"61ce2a5b16f5">access_level (who can view: all, parents only)=
</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"35305a546bce" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Storage&amp;SecurityRequirements">Storage &amp=
; Security Requirements</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"736c2da8-f061-40df-9716-0685dd9ff736">
<li local-id=3D"2409f903-268d-4b6c-ae61-70e692916d62">
<p local-id=3D"99dd891e19a3">Google Cloud Storage for file hosting (100GB f=
ree tier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7c9a9ce2-b275-46f0-9c7a-c422880788e1">
<p local-id=3D"75e324f98ed1">End-to-end encryption for sensitive documents<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c81349ff-b0e1-4889-878e-517c26c1f78d">
<p local-id=3D"cc0b6dcb4dab">GDPR compliant: Data stored in EU region</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"61ee423d-d0d9-4c17-ab06-ce721656a0fc">
<p local-id=3D"336efe88b2f5">Audit log: Track who accessed which documents<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"2d864fcca34a" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DeferredtoPost-MVP.5">Deferred to Post-MVP</h3=
>
<ul local-id=3D"7f5b0053-1632-4981-ac76-7c19ebea4cbf">
<li local-id=3D"36df6ac2-e252-4b39-b1b8-fc6e1155c896">
<p local-id=3D"530061dff89a">OCR text extraction for scanned documents</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"c9640e8e-9157-4a98-b21f-38f7f9d0e6a5">
<p local-id=3D"39766e1373e2">AI-powered document categorization</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"708d87bb-d97c-474a-acab-071abd5fa8a2">
<p local-id=3D"53671cb95823">Version control for documents</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2ff6338-4758-464e-99e1-b8831b06c817">
<p local-id=3D"4133141a677b">Document sharing with external parties (doctor=
s, schools)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff30b11f-d7cb-4895-98e8-f525597ccd1b">
<p local-id=3D"e092cb2ed48d">Bulk upload and organization</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"6c96e86918cb"></p>
<p local-id=3D"a76757a031fb"></p>
<h2 local-id=3D"8d45b2dc8b3c" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.7MealPlanner">4.7 Meal Planner</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"bd1330648cab" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FirstPrincipleAnalysis.6">First Principle Anal=
ysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"482fde8d7220">Fundamental Truth: Families must eat daily, re=
quiring planning (what to cook), shopping (ingredients), and preparation (r=
ecipes). The daily question "What's for dinner?" creates decision fatigue.<=
/p>
<h3 local-id=3D"c9430cbc0450" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CoreUserNeed.6">Core User Need</h3>
<p local-id=3D"c7131d3369f9">Plan meals in advance to reduce daily decision=
 fatigue, generate grocery lists automatically, and access recipes easily d=
uring cooking.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"93ad0370d744" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MVPFeatures(PriorityP0-MustHave).6">MVP Featur=
es (Priority P0 - Must Have)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"126e76d8-8e91-414e-8a3e-d98ea0a203a9">
<li local-id=3D"8e136b08-c691-4701-99a8-c4af515a2bbe">
<p local-id=3D"0241dac9b3b5">Weekly Meal Calendar: 7-day view with breakfas=
t, lunch, dinner slots</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4ade722-723a-4d5e-8b36-647418dae9c2">
<p local-id=3D"8d4991c79ebb">Meal Assignment: Drag or add meals to specific=
 days/times</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f70a39cd-672c-4f7d-a4df-d46ccf4ef7fc">
<p local-id=3D"4c7926a44663">Recipe Library: Store favorite recipes with in=
gredients and instructions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8298f4b2-24e9-4a1f-9569-13a2c8c2732e">
<p local-id=3D"cff3405a3548">Grocery List Generation: Auto-generate shoppin=
g list from meal plan</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"23296632-eb88-4359-8887-573b8d440a81">
<p local-id=3D"c1e6c593475a">Recipe Creation: Add custom recipes (title, in=
gredients, steps, servings)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1a7d3bb8-b460-49d5-848b-1cd9f0b51b88">
<p local-id=3D"31c7853dc3df">Recipe Search: Search recipes by name or ingre=
dient</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d851ae67-47da-4c2c-82eb-f1b1b46d89e9">
<p local-id=3D"c21dd11ea149">Leftover Tracking: Mark meals as "leftover" to=
 prevent waste</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"959d9d70-2389-4fe4-8a81-2df4fae07326">
<p local-id=3D"fba675901fdb">Serving Adjustment: Scale recipe quantities fo=
r different serving sizes</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6eeb44b15029" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceCommands(MealAgent)">Voice Commands (Meal=
 Agent)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"63a91e69-6bd1-41a4-9acf-d60b766fc420">
<li local-id=3D"bbb4e814-9e7e-4caf-9c45-8c3cc7dc93fc">
<p local-id=3D"d0fad0af36ef">"Add spaghetti carbonara to Monday dinner"</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"ee4a600a-3996-4dd9-a48f-d28f775fb851">
<p local-id=3D"8ebd40bdcba5">"What's for dinner tonight?"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"376ec51c-f122-4b90-8b21-2ab2a0e9899f">
<p local-id=3D"53c54570ac42">"Show me chicken recipes"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c48b6bdb-894a-486d-8917-a9b740d54538">
<p local-id=3D"f56eb78af023">"Generate grocery list for this week"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4a2c93a4-c6a8-4839-b13a-abd2518f3176">
<p local-id=3D"cbce18f54e60">"Plan meals for next week"</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"75223da29baf" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AutomaticUpdates&amp;Notifications.6">Automati=
c Updates &amp; Notifications</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"1475fa4c-2fc2-483b-ae96-3cdee4c9aae1">
<li local-id=3D"44ec2348-bce5-4f35-bfb1-1b6a7d4d0607">
<p local-id=3D"dab8b6408a22">Sunday evening reminder to plan next week's me=
als</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c032d688-9d60-42f8-b979-af69f78c6290">
<p local-id=3D"951f868408cf">Morning notification of today's planned meals<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e25c7da-101b-4dd2-8305-58af59f2e33e">
<p local-id=3D"d23afcc60597">Grocery list notification if shopping day is a=
pproaching</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"1c7b4bf5bcfb" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataModel(FirstPrinciples).6">Data Model (Firs=
t Principles)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a050913a9099">Recipe Entity:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e9323cf4-a8a7-4d83-9f2f-cb24f6547886">
<li local-id=3D"62fe6905-a99d-4033-8bc4-3a0b0b6e89dd">
<p local-id=3D"5d14415cdc75">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4af39ca3-fe59-4c74-bf46-451fbe8069ec">
<p local-id=3D"dab0ab3c9baf">title (recipe name)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f4123baa-5f47-42e3-bdc8-cebb3040ebaa">
<p local-id=3D"b31f4144c1e0">description (brief description)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e3f34759-ed3c-4c9a-9b6b-824c6b9535f1">
<p local-id=3D"d09abcedac5e">ingredients[] (array of ingredient objects)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba6114b0-ef93-4446-b7e2-3afc8407ecdb">
<p local-id=3D"3bb23a0cf765">instructions[] (array of cooking steps)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"0589201a-9d16-405b-b43c-1ad0644e087e">
<p local-id=3D"df05e42e8843">servings (number of servings)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d023959-85cd-480d-8759-70a57fafdd09">
<p local-id=3D"db69a4efb1a5">prep_time (minutes)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b3bf9f06-1cf1-42de-b0b9-277e688ebb4e">
<p local-id=3D"2bbb6da0d9b2">cook_time (minutes)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4dd2b453-7b84-48ec-903d-d87b2f71e2e2">
<p local-id=3D"6cf5c277cb13">tags[] (cuisine type, dietary restrictions)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb5e15be-e7d2-4352-b3c5-887c5ea54f16">
<p local-id=3D"d0bc76193e78">image_url (recipe photo)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"29b79bf6-8687-4d9c-b27c-cf6524a0b13e">
<p local-id=3D"55800ee0886d">created_by (family member ID)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"93484fb629f5">Meal Plan Entry:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b9c4fb45-a6c6-4539-ad0c-e25286f6b2c4">
<li local-id=3D"f77934c2-e844-4f43-9edc-08bceac90baa">
<p local-id=3D"8e59903ff252">id (unique identifier)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"304d3422-d910-46f0-af39-399e4f7fe01b">
<p local-id=3D"b19ae6f37ccd">date (which day)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cb124be-ce5a-4c58-9dd7-38ddfdb1db9b">
<p local-id=3D"377b21e7a95c">meal_time (breakfast, lunch, dinner)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2a5c7ed-3a88-4780-a7fe-c6570cdcb421">
<p local-id=3D"592b2f894b0d">recipe_id (which recipe)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b3b1159d-bd90-40af-8b61-807d8df60815">
<p local-id=3D"3490bfb04913">is_leftover (boolean)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d3df0a1-c8e2-4b91-a465-45c8706cdaff">
<p local-id=3D"3ba00fcc8202">notes (meal-specific notes)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"9797eb89632d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AIMealAgentCapabilities(Premium)">AI Meal Agen=
t Capabilities (Premium)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"e14a48d7-97b2-4d96-a54e-fd21948fcef1">
<li local-id=3D"9f2e652a-d943-423e-8664-104b442c04a9">
<p local-id=3D"ababcf12c0ee">Recipe suggestions based on family preferences=
 and dietary needs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8a0a7a05-f6a9-4068-b55d-efe3832e2e30">
<p local-id=3D"0d6c653b0d1e">Automatic meal plan generation for the week</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"2499402d-847f-4abb-b0d3-f085cb568c3a">
<p local-id=3D"1cd7bc6eebde">Ingredient substitution suggestions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eaf9f170-5c50-41b2-adb7-6c14804e2a65">
<p local-id=3D"9ec8a5a8ecb7">Nutritional analysis and recommendations</p></=
li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"1e1c2c596f84" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DeferredtoPost-MVP.6">Deferred to Post-MVP</h3=
>
<ul local-id=3D"e216236a-6388-42a9-bb4b-49ecdb453bab">
<li local-id=3D"44a3abd4-f97f-483b-b5d3-ed807e0e39f5">
<p local-id=3D"d047a36b35f1">Integration with recipe websites (import recip=
es from URL)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e89c5491-cf6b-4e01-9573-3c2ce9911026">
<p local-id=3D"e64c2ff68386">Nutritional information and calorie tracking</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3768afef-f4f5-4af1-998d-a2e5357fe970">
<p local-id=3D"d9cc9bdbc51a">Dietary restriction filtering (vegetarian, glu=
ten-free, etc.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"923b820a-48a5-4534-9f91-f19b76ec4f08">
<p local-id=3D"af25dc95f640">Meal prep mode with batch cooking features</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"933a1ed6-fc19-49ee-9ad5-f042f69b70d7">
<p local-id=3D"37e8abe52a82">Integration with grocery delivery services</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"4303885f-f1dc-4fdc-8118-b63d572bcc67">
<p local-id=3D"106c4164a00e">Family favorites and most-cooked tracking</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c5008326c556"></p>
<p local-id=3D"a04ad4889851"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"6681a58aa85d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-5.AIAgentArchitecture">5. AI Agent Architectur=
e</h1>
<p local-id=3D"0674dfc5e373">The AI system is the core differentiator of th=
e Family OS. Rather than a single monolithic AI, the system uses a multi-ag=
ent architecture with specialized agents for each domain, orchestrated by a=
 central coordinator.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"bbb04e54d193" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-ArchitecturePattern:AgentOrchestration">Archit=
ecture Pattern: Agent Orchestration</h2>
<p local-id=3D"206abc73a89b">The system implements three communication patt=
erns:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"73fd99ea-774f-4cb1-97ae-f2a0cf3aa59a">
<li local-id=3D"8635c98a-1a44-4937-959f-dda68551cd45">
<p local-id=3D"817b4a3d1f28">MCP (Model Context Protocol): Agents access st=
ructured context about family data</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c9acad11-eb68-418f-bd3e-165f3552d87b">
<p local-id=3D"62cdf60ce628">A2UI (Agent-to-UI): Agents can update UI eleme=
nts and trigger actions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4daa23d6-725e-43c0-ac9c-bf086f2092df">
<p local-id=3D"1d9c6da45246">A2A (Agent-to-Agent): Agents can coordinate wi=
th each other for complex tasks</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"74b058b271c1" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-OrchestratorAgent(Gemini3.0Pro)">Orchestrator =
Agent (Gemini 3.0 Pro)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"5a323e82d8b5">Role: Central coordinator and router for all u=
ser interactions</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"96bb3ff5463d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Responsibilities:">Responsibilities:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"e2cdc77a-4dd7-4d9c-ba3c-d8f76c2d7b22">
<li local-id=3D"353cbc00-3456-42e0-9afa-c22936f8fdfa">
<p local-id=3D"4fadf4ef9d33">Intent Detection: Determine which specialist a=
gent to invoke</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8eded8d6-60b4-479b-9f81-25be59e2d408">
<p local-id=3D"970d31efa251">Multi-Agent Coordination: For complex queries =
spanning multiple domains</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6fdf03b5-84b2-4082-8288-078c9351fc3d">
<p local-id=3D"ec404c4012bc">Context Management: Maintain conversation stat=
e and family context</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c5f8289-1d78-43b3-b910-1849f71f89d4">
<p local-id=3D"4d0f542064d1">Response Synthesis: Combine outputs from multi=
ple agents into coherent response</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b5a233d-5f5d-4cd3-89b6-582599fd82fa">
<p local-id=3D"b2972ca0ab0b">Fallback Handling: Handle queries that don't f=
it specialist agents</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"15dee0ff2510" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-ExampleFlows:">Example Flows:</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ae1ccc32da87">User: "Plan our family trip next month"<br>
Orchestrator =E2=86=92 Calendar Agent (check availability) =E2=86=92 Task A=
gent (create packing tasks) =E2=86=92 Feed Agent (post trip announcement) =
=E2=86=92 Response to user</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"f479c721b443" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-SpecialistAgents(Gemini2.0Flash)">Specialist A=
gents (Gemini 2.0 Flash)</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"236cccbf9491" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-1.CalendarAgent">1. Calendar Agent</h3>
<p local-id=3D"dd178fd6bf94">Domain: Time, scheduling, events, appointments=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"86cb01d4-999d-4f38-96df-8f96a50db9b0">
<li local-id=3D"92704d31-8b16-4c38-8a89-f14f2cdf25cc">
<p local-id=3D"00e0c3560857">Add/edit/delete events</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a30fe980-4915-4f48-935b-bb8d37104ef9">
<p local-id=3D"d297f8c37bce">Find schedule conflicts</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cf22d18-6cc5-4862-8c03-021036051ae8">
<p local-id=3D"cde98442bc3f">Answer "when" questions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a97deb77-492c-4d61-95eb-886a325038a2">
<p local-id=3D"6241e9c6da28">Suggest optimal meeting times</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"00c412ec91dd" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-2.TaskAgent">2. Task Agent</h3>
<p local-id=3D"fa7a835b3eec">Domain: Responsibilities, chores, to-dos, assi=
gnments</p>
<ul local-id=3D"99e71664-04eb-4025-a0cb-16a9fff18c04">
<li local-id=3D"58c2bd49-f49a-4dbe-b611-edaab896962c">
<p local-id=3D"b5eba745df10">Create and assign tasks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21a1b059-38e4-47d9-91f1-46670565299d">
<p local-id=3D"c380e843b3c5">Track completion status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9be2761a-5b51-416c-b225-0e59aef26ca3">
<p local-id=3D"0e36061e1fd5">Balance workload distribution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6b2eb651-3822-4cca-b1ea-3b38db8b1f0e">
<p local-id=3D"2b36f9253562">Suggest task priorities</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"cdd2e1f65c8c" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-3.ListAgent">3. List Agent</h3>
<p local-id=3D"fb0ad8894337">Domain: Shared lists, groceries, shopping, inv=
entory</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6edf3088-9556-4e0f-be1c-762ae77b540c">
<li local-id=3D"4a59ce01-f4c8-46ca-83d5-ce74232c2fff">
<p local-id=3D"d76f23112644">Add/remove list items</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"75e68bd9-ca95-4690-808f-9c572d7ac7c6">
<p local-id=3D"fffd60a5ea65">Manage multiple lists</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16db4881-739b-47f6-b382-a541e8fcfbdc">
<p local-id=3D"042ae51dd8c3">Suggest list categories</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"25b9e327-8801-4c4c-a42a-c7193ee4aff7">
<p local-id=3D"0bf0760ab5ac">Track purchase history</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"f6137c29d3d4" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.FinanceAgent(Gemini3.0Pro-AccuracyCritical)"=
>4. Finance Agent (Gemini 3.0 Pro - Accuracy Critical)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"071baf14419f">Domain: Money, expenses, budgets, financial an=
alysis</p>
<ul local-id=3D"92a45a74-3fb9-445c-bae4-efb9bc9dfb96">
<li local-id=3D"62c4e9a8-fddf-4dbd-a19c-b51f36be950e">
<p local-id=3D"ab7714524d12">Log expenses with automatic categorization</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"7fb9d39e-5fe5-4af8-86a7-cf0243263f65">
<p local-id=3D"b78cbea40d34">Track budget vs. actual spending</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9943fb5b-f686-435a-9851-4e22ae876b9c">
<p local-id=3D"45bfc5d0e34a">Generate financial insights and alerts</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"1008eb56-df52-4ed2-b6b4-970f498053f1">
<p local-id=3D"6db95e70b264">Detect unusual spending patterns</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"81039f31e322" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-5.FeedAgent">5. Feed Agent</h3>
<p local-id=3D"db53db4bc306">Domain: Communication, updates, posts, announc=
ements</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8236d73f-e48d-4bbe-b4ff-d2d36953eda1">
<li local-id=3D"0a278133-a588-4b34-88e9-a1ca4a1200aa">
<p local-id=3D"a7ee8c71f83a">Create posts from voice input</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d055f96b-53cc-4f0d-ae0c-452260518984">
<p local-id=3D"946637a515bb">Summarize recent family updates</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"87a9840a-90e2-4032-894a-397b1b75a272">
<p local-id=3D"2962e570a885">Add comments via voice</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"412697c8-e930-4fed-98db-9cd6e9924cda">
<p local-id=3D"c735582e697b">Suggest relevant responses</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"a94f87bbf6ca" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-6.DocumentAgent">6. Document Agent</h3>
<p local-id=3D"28c7084e6aa3">Domain: Files, documents, storage, retrieval</=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"216affa9-8bcf-45f8-a387-03ec4a0692fc">
<li local-id=3D"7b0ef483-705b-491d-9656-26ba961c1cb5">
<p local-id=3D"f36da23e5e68">Upload and categorize documents</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"316166a0-4aac-414b-847b-a2aa9f3e5ffa">
<p local-id=3D"d2e768271dad">Search and retrieve files</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afadbc6e-39be-4a1c-8deb-994ca8845d78">
<p local-id=3D"b425f165424b">Suggest organization structure</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"58968a5e-19de-4372-afa5-87b65b72d690">
<p local-id=3D"61c74c6e0340">Extract key information from documents</p></li=
>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"db28f4cbe2c2" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-7.MealAgent">7. Meal Agent</h3>
<p local-id=3D"8a6932512a22">Domain: Food, recipes, meal planning, grocerie=
s</p>
<ul local-id=3D"549bd097-0116-4c46-be7d-0977bb8e2537">
<li local-id=3D"e2438acc-ef02-42b3-81bf-cb29c28c9dbe">
<p local-id=3D"2fe0126684a5">Plan weekly meals</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3b6bbe1d-e529-4d74-a88e-dacd0071a6de">
<p local-id=3D"0cdf96977c4c">Suggest recipes based on preferences</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e4b65446-a3d7-4c66-9d25-485ef75b87d0">
<p local-id=3D"d9dfed1d290a">Generate grocery lists from meal plans</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"7f3f9ed2-d288-41e0-b871-2a6987b358d8">
<p local-id=3D"c2a376ec5eb3">Track dietary restrictions and preferences</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"8d61c2a4efac" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceInput/OutputImplementation">Voice Input/O=
utput Implementation</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"e815a8818f9d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceInput(expo-av-On-device,Free)">Voice Inpu=
t (expo-av - On-device, Free)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"bed30029-8172-4449-a4b4-53b84494fe95">
<li local-id=3D"20043a21-7288-4126-a2b4-9e8f9953a532">
<p local-id=3D"38fb3ea02282">Speech-to-text using device native API</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"27a39637-9085-47dc-8ca0-11cafb9b89f9">
<p local-id=3D"595223b00aff">No cloud costs, privacy-preserving</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d04bdd9c-d3cf-4ae7-b8d3-413e6ddad715">
<p local-id=3D"08b43a43b041">Real-time transcription with visual feedback</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6418ddd9-f392-4580-bf5a-66d116da5cef">
<p local-id=3D"dcd76cd649a7">Support for EU languages: English, German, Fre=
nch, Spanish, Italian</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"e5b346493482" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-VoiceOutput(expo-speech-On-device,Free)">Voice=
 Output (expo-speech - On-device, Free)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"fe8c5b45-321e-4740-b993-6f9e716c91d5">
<li local-id=3D"e3d1c9f6-f734-4d07-afff-eb03570f0720">
<p local-id=3D"9fc3a6dc1dcc">Text-to-speech using device native API</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"46c5d0c8-68ca-46f6-8e23-7d6f494b5ab3">
<p local-id=3D"ca875868ab99">No cloud costs, works offline</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d069c01f-131c-44d0-ace3-e37e87fd0e3c">
<p local-id=3D"b0289baf581a">Natural-sounding voices in user's language</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"9a2f6552-f660-4bec-bce5-d3d38890a33c">
<p local-id=3D"1eb760da7ae2">Adjustable speed and pitch</p></li>
</ul>
