<p local-id=3D"3b41d39e6a05"></p>
<p local-id=3D"762bbd4fcc99">Expected Monthly AI Cost per Family (100 voice=
 interactions): ~$1.50 - $3.00<br>
Free tier includes 50 interactions/month. Premium unlimited at $9.99/month.=
</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"ebfcbc193151" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AgentCommunicationExamples">Agent Communicatio=
n Examples</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"2b282686f18d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Example1:SimpleSingle-AgentRequest">Example 1:=
 Simple Single-Agent Request</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1fea406a2f95">User: "Add milk to the grocery list"<br>
Flow: Orchestrator =E2=86=92 List Agent =E2=86=92 Update Database =E2=86=92=
 Confirm to User</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"d206951a3447" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Example2:Multi-AgentCoordination">Example 2: M=
ulti-Agent Coordination</h3>
<p local-id=3D"6fd94946a5fc">User: "We're having friends over for dinner Fr=
iday night"<br>
Flow:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"28b2505b5023">
<li local-id=3D"fef2a3937257">
<p local-id=3D"61931e332ea5">Orchestrator analyzes intent (event + meal)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"934bcdfd6780">
<p local-id=3D"15e3afd07a39">Calendar Agent: Add "Dinner with friends" even=
t Friday 7pm</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"289ec6dd0422">
<p local-id=3D"8ef9bc14d2b2">Meal Agent: Suggest recipes for 6 people, add =
to meal plan</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2e09c8dc0b9">
<p local-id=3D"2b73b694db5b">List Agent: Add ingredients to grocery list</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"d6803c9c05fa">
<p local-id=3D"049323193784">Feed Agent: Post announcement "We're hosting d=
inner Friday!"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9353c2231b9e">
<p local-id=3D"cbf4fc4a36f9">Orchestrator: Synthesize response confirming a=
ll actions</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"8d5887d76bf2"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"bb022ab59ab5" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-6.UserRoles&amp;Permissions">6. User Roles &am=
p; Permissions</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"faaf26f398d4" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FirstPrinciple:DifferentFamilyMembersNeedDiffe=
rentAccess">First Principle: Different Family Members Need Different Access=
</h2>
<p local-id=3D"15a494caef26">Families contain people of different ages, mat=
urity levels, and responsibilities. Children should not have access to fina=
ncial information or sensitive documents. Parents need administrative contr=
ol.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"5d65372f9b3a" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-RoleDefinitions">Role Definitions</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"a338c77d8de8" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Parent/AdminRole">Parent/Admin Role</h3>
<p local-id=3D"52389190edac">Age: 18+</p>
<p local-id=3D"def93b50bd5c">Permissions: Full access to all modules and se=
ttings</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9c52aa35-c974-4b17-91d3-c2459a760ae3">
<li local-id=3D"0fb61afc-b6f9-4fe3-883b-0f557f06ab1a">
<p local-id=3D"0dcc59c0e302">Calendar: Full CRUD (create, read, update, del=
ete)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ed4394b0-3852-4134-a887-2c0da4118eff">
<p local-id=3D"d2b9ad2c5ff5">Tasks: Assign to anyone, view all tasks, edit =
all tasks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cf362e26-7c29-47ee-86dd-26680396b923">
<p local-id=3D"ea5d73c64238">Lists: Full access to all lists</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c18ae05b-222f-4cde-a938-0cbdc92e7f8e">
<p local-id=3D"760ee88016b0">Expenses: Add/edit/delete all expenses, view a=
ll budgets</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a91b5ea2-3e2d-4fc7-a0e7-60717fc9f72c">
<p local-id=3D"d39611495f6f">Feed: Post, comment, delete own and others' po=
sts (moderation)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"533f305d-e75c-41ee-9b76-fcd45ad43828">
<p local-id=3D"60d9e37a2d8e">Documents: Upload, view, delete, set access le=
vels</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"93eaed44-4bd1-4e9a-869b-ea0c1f6efd41">
<p local-id=3D"b1175be55f66">Meal Plan: Full access to plan, add recipes, g=
enerate lists</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc906a5c-2d2e-4296-bd2d-7eff28c4d7c5">
<p local-id=3D"38ada5e9fd37">Settings: Manage family members, roles, subscr=
iptions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3431f6ec-7fcc-4b35-8b75-cefe8cd3b012">
<p local-id=3D"0e53d1180c04">AI Agents: Access all AI features and voice co=
mmands</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"b9f38a075884" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Child/LimitedRole">Child/Limited Role</h3>
<p local-id=3D"6a4dda3e6d3a">Age: Under 18 (or designated as limited by par=
ent)</p>
<p local-id=3D"75734bcd4f99">Permissions: Restricted access, age-appropriat=
e</p>
<ul local-id=3D"49678b2c-301b-4d06-b241-8ac3051d040d">
<li local-id=3D"2e806216-6689-47ba-94b3-d88f716224df">
<p local-id=3D"e1cba159a379">Calendar: View family calendar, cannot delete =
others' events</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3f7aeb06-c36e-4b3e-8f11-3b6bfb8e50ce">
<p local-id=3D"5070d1aab8f2">Tasks: View assigned tasks, mark own tasks com=
plete, cannot assign tasks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"72211c4c-68eb-45ce-91d6-26f9f4c6b219">
<p local-id=3D"f340ef9b0940">Lists: Add items, check off items, cannot dele=
te lists</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cb05f12a-e76a-4417-b762-54355cf820db">
<p local-id=3D"18808a7a91ac">Expenses: NO ACCESS (financial data hidden)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"18ab35c9-cb9e-4604-a127-f4a31b025588">
<p local-id=3D"3af936b6ce36">Feed: Post and comment (parent moderation opti=
onal)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"530b32ed-a170-4f98-86a6-bce86c98eae1">
<p local-id=3D"97c91ee6bab9">Documents: Access only documents marked "acces=
sible to children"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0db0cd8d-01a3-4fec-8232-5aa080005107">
<p local-id=3D"8b52f0060d9a">Meal Plan: View meal plan, cannot edit</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"a3c28a15-ac6b-4771-b8e2-10f04fdb792e">
<p local-id=3D"9e243ff91c51">Settings: NO ACCESS (cannot change settings)</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6ef4c7c9-19af-497c-9db9-90c31cd58803">
<p local-id=3D"17720f86979c">AI Agents: Limited voice commands (no financia=
l or document queries)</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"6148e3a67052" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FamilySetup&amp;Onboarding">Family Setup &amp;=
 Onboarding</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"599192638aa6" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AccountCreationFlow">Account Creation Flow</h3=
>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"35083df7-78ba-446e-86a6-85d50815409c">
<li local-id=3D"5d0a791a-da17-4707-8fd9-13dd83c96757">
<p local-id=3D"414bb718521b">Step 1: First parent creates account (automati=
cally becomes Admin)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5171856c-729e-4b2b-bbeb-8fc05e29a1a0">
<p local-id=3D"fe2beb1e928d">Step 2: Parent invites partner/spouse (granted=
 Admin role)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4e9d6b4-ea32-4bba-9527-bd402e2fc310">
<p local-id=3D"65462f6c91b8">Step 3: Parents add children (assigned Limited=
 role, set age)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"77699d02-b8a2-497b-8313-75d4985115a1">
<p local-id=3D"34613f206d29">Step 4: Configure notification preferences per=
 person</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73711e00-ecab-49ec-b627-18930aa2a2fb">
<p local-id=3D"2b25cd1d24d4">Step 5: Tutorial walkthrough of each module</p=
></li>
</ol>
<h3 local-id=3D"73b347d52d07" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-PermissionOverrides(FutureConsideration)">Perm=
ission Overrides (Future Consideration)</h3>
<p local-id=3D"dd3a9f14379d">Post-MVP: Allow custom permission levels betwe=
en Parent and Child (e.g., teenager with expense tracking access but not do=
cument access).</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"6bcbd3906a9c" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Security&amp;PrivacySafeguards">Security &amp;=
 Privacy Safeguards</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"f5815c57-f627-41a6-9417-5d44fe4a19f6">
<li local-id=3D"e1b91c2e-3e36-4612-a3af-e0cc8d932051">
<p local-id=3D"57ab96afa3ee">Each family member has individual login creden=
tials</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8586b65-c203-4023-81ac-19c83cab8ba9">
<p local-id=3D"f55b5b9897e0">PIN or biometric lock for app access (optional=
 setting)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbef2933-fb8a-4af2-ac06-2a63ca9359be">
<p local-id=3D"95aafe2268c7">Audit log: Parents can see who accessed what a=
nd when</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"795efe8d-2ab0-4fcc-ad25-03d8914583a2">
<p local-id=3D"085216f1de58">Children cannot delete audit logs or modify ac=
cess settings</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0a9eca91-35fd-4c15-8838-7f0fc05bd464">
<p local-id=3D"945da3264b24">Emergency access: One parent can lock other fa=
mily members out if needed</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"f5d7c7b89935" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-7.MVPFeaturePrioritization">7. MVP Feature Pri=
oritization</h1>
<p local-id=3D"36084f20b184">Features are prioritized using the MoSCoW meth=
od (Must Have, Should Have, Could Have, Won't Have for MVP) based on: (1) C=
ritical user need, (2) Technical feasibility within 10 weeks, (3) Different=
iation value.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"37873c75a2d4" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MustHave(P0)-CoreMVP">Must Have (P0) - Core MV=
P</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0d3b29e4f124">These features define the product and must be =
in MVP.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6d1f91af-3519-4842-9f9d-a430c6b53816">
<li local-id=3D"52e98097-2a37-4010-bf4e-a901c571c131">
<p local-id=3D"063e5691c51a">Calendar: Shared calendar, event CRUD, recurri=
ng events, reminders, conflict detection</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a5946158-a0f7-440e-8753-6c46d65b1bd2">
<p local-id=3D"91a197fac74f">Tasks: Task CRUD, assignment, status tracking,=
 recurring tasks, due dates</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"047b158d-38a9-4aa2-860a-570b3bc43a21">
<p local-id=3D"347ffcc54e63">Lists: Multiple lists, real-time sync, check-o=
ff, offline access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b175d2c5-cf4b-4916-acb2-e187463f160e">
<p local-id=3D"555a0aebff09">Expenses: Manual entry, categories, budgets, a=
lerts, receipt photos</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d63090f9-4ca9-4dbd-adea-6079df9cd388">
<p local-id=3D"66867f8a6d36">Feed: Posts, comments, reactions, chronologica=
l feed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3a63528-93e6-49fd-be62-9c1b1038cdb7">
<p local-id=3D"58925e87b49d">Documents: Upload, categorize, search, preview=
, encryption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"099f9f29-98c4-4c63-a46e-ac6497d23ff3">
<p local-id=3D"ffa35cd00069">Meal Plan: Weekly view, recipe library, grocer=
y list generation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b43859b7-07f0-4e90-b6a5-59f179da70ed">
<p local-id=3D"5137232938b6">Voice Input: Speech-to-text for all modules vi=
a expo-av</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5c4f514-be2e-4d5b-a746-33ea4697759f">
<p local-id=3D"1c212f06b457">AI Orchestrator: Route requests to specialist =
agents</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d5037be3-c043-4ce9-8090-2a2fc1664b7c">
<p local-id=3D"c9eed939c1da">User Roles: Parent (admin) and Child (limited)=
 permissions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"87c573b3-a49c-49b9-bbd2-fe72683fc742">
<p local-id=3D"2accdf77b857">Notifications: Push notifications for reminder=
s and updates</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9e1b3e60-1a39-486d-9d40-d481289aa2a8">
<p local-id=3D"6393020550b3">Offline Mode: Calendar and lists viewable/edit=
able offline</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"f861b7add982" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-ShouldHave(P1)-ImportantbutNotBlocking">Should=
 Have (P1) - Important but Not Blocking</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f95525871d47">Include if time permits, defer to v1.1 if nece=
ssary.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"29c2d3a3-f195-45ee-ae95-2ca04c5b67d6">
<li local-id=3D"08b08f6a-e11e-4f20-9e2d-e67761f54239">
<p local-id=3D"589f5d6933ba">Voice Output: Text-to-speech responses via exp=
o-speech</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c6c7f4b9-54fd-4382-bcc4-37d16edc57af">
<p local-id=3D"4a51ea0cf2eb">Family Dashboard: Overview widget showing toda=
y's schedule, tasks, expenses</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f238f4e-2723-4135-afd5-e8083b51747c">
<p local-id=3D"5aafc7b17f1f">Spending Charts: Visual pie charts and trend g=
raphs for expenses</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ce61d56-f610-496d-bf27-a8a1e5617892">
<p local-id=3D"d10bf8a7cd3e">Task Analytics: Completion rate and workload d=
istribution insights</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d0fca416-319e-4a88-954c-88b9d99f0aaa">
<p local-id=3D"24925dbcd3d8">Recipe Photos: Image upload for recipes in mea=
l planner</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b66413e6-99de-471e-a1b1-a791c66afcb4">
<p local-id=3D"e948361a2ece">Multi-language Support: English, German, Frenc=
h, Spanish</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"98b87208-59df-4bfd-b5cc-634790cdbe60">
<p local-id=3D"678b85f72e7a">Dark Mode: UI theme toggle</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"fe1dbb34c27b" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CouldHave(P2)-NicetoHave">Could Have (P2) - Ni=
ce to Have</h2>
<p local-id=3D"d84e262abce8">Enhance user experience but not essential for =
MVP.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9bac14cc-f195-4e28-bdeb-066ffc4b3915">
<li local-id=3D"ca78099f-c9e6-4810-958e-ac4fbf91045c">
<p local-id=3D"d57004cd90ac">Calendar Sync: Import/export to Google Calenda=
r, Apple Calendar</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"95eecc94-30cd-472b-9243-431d3c465734">
<p local-id=3D"55dae2e5ec1a">Chore Rotation: Auto-assign rotating chores fa=
irly</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"759b1264-49a8-4812-95dd-58e353f89c8f">
<p local-id=3D"eab7353bdd0e">Recipe Import: Import recipes from URLs</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"f716d320-3897-4ed1-a5c5-61f10f0fc7aa">
<p local-id=3D"026bcd095bc5">Photo Albums: Dedicated photo albums in Feed</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c2d29f54-a163-4dcb-905b-2af1dbae2dc9">
<p local-id=3D"e8b75d30efc4">Widgets: Home screen widgets for iOS/Android</=
p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"94573231ba69" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Won'tHave(P3)-Post-MVP">Won't Have (P3) - Post=
-MVP</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a300f5f442fa">Explicitly deferred to future releases.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"890a4712-4835-463a-b8d2-9c93546ca309">
<li local-id=3D"f2e5cf1c-3c93-4e84-a6c2-f5e2ba952be4">
<p local-id=3D"50f55d3aee6c">Bank Integration: Automatic transaction import=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5ca057a8-b9fc-4e65-bb8b-8bea84ba923e">
<p local-id=3D"e4b33032913c">OCR Document Scanning: Extract text from scann=
ed docs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22e8fa3f-779a-4ee9-bc38-3f445e2dcfb4">
<p local-id=3D"c866f5d3a4f8">Video Posts: Video upload in Family Feed</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"14e80a76-7cf1-4d7e-9dd7-12ff021b198b">
<p local-id=3D"81dee9b31e5e">Goal Tracking: Financial and personal goal set=
ting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a75e557f-cccf-4e16-be3f-a895c6e60dc8">
<p local-id=3D"3645c2023d04">Third-Party Integrations: Spotify, Netflix, ot=
her apps</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d0e4b68-b0d2-4702-8060-f1560d39114f">
<p local-id=3D"0ff171945358">Web Version: Desktop/web app (mobile-only for =
MVP)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"886e791f-05ec-4fbc-ac00-1be910e64ebb">
<p local-id=3D"d26a5f912fb4">Advanced AI: Predictive scheduling, proactive =
suggestions</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"550600d1df43" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MVPFeatureScopeJustification">MVP Feature Scop=
e Justification</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7dd6da166838">The MVP includes 7 core modules with essential=
 features in each. This scope is achievable in 10 weeks with a focused team=
 and provides enough value to validate product-market fit. Voice interactio=
n is the key differentiator and is prioritized heavily. Offline access for =
Calendar and Lists ensures usability in low-connectivity situations common =
in Europe (trains, rural areas).</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"e81827a4ff6e" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-8.TechnicalArchitecture">8. Technical Architec=
ture</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"f99400cb68d3" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-SystemArchitectureOverview">System Architectur=
e Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"1c3234eac3e8">The Family OS follows a mobile-first architect=
ure with a React Native frontend, Bun-powered backend API, PostgreSQL datab=
ase, and AI orchestration layer.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"416cb2e1bee0" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FrontendArchitecture">Frontend Architecture</h=
2>
<h3 local-id=3D"5f7e85b1dc5e" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-MobileApplicationStack">Mobile Application Sta=
ck</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"4bb3e345-bfdc-4ffd-8513-08eb7eca5cf7">
<li local-id=3D"92db22a4-a1b0-49e9-bbad-9c136e753636">
<p local-id=3D"9dbd22d679ea">Framework: React Native (Expo SDK 51+)</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"0291d67c-8cf5-4dda-911c-05be8b969766">
<p local-id=3D"dd370a60029a">Language: TypeScript 5.x (strict mode),i18n</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"3c7da30d-a96e-4cce-b99c-981ad0646ab7">
<p local-id=3D"510f0a41b5fa">Navigation: Expo Router (file-based routing)</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"776298bd-25a7-4a34-9a39-9781caed3001">
<p local-id=3D"e2c751216e7d">State Management: Zustand (lightweight, simple=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1393ba1e-a6fd-4ad1-ac13-6f71cadda143">
<p local-id=3D"636d4bde8d1e">UI Components: React Native Paper + Custom Com=
ponents</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae4f2ed3-56e3-49f7-85be-68a25f94f79a">
<p local-id=3D"2716be71ae2b">Animations: React Native Reanimated 3.x</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"80324b9e-abab-4844-98a1-97fe62a84db5">
<p local-id=3D"3d3baad5815e">API Client: tRPC Client 10.x (end-to-end type =
safety)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0fec67bb-bced-4b6b-96ec-68ecae7199cb">
<p local-id=3D"d92646dd3634">Voice Input: expo-av (on-device speech-to-text=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"028caa94-60d1-435d-8f33-bde17c35ecf1">
<p local-id=3D"6368009e66c8">Voice Output: expo-speech (on-device text-to-s=
peech)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"730eab83-ca71-4ede-b4ef-99a904561eaa">
<p local-id=3D"d8c7578097ab">Offline Storage: Expo SQLite + AsyncStorage</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"91042310-e28d-4813-9cc7-59117f48a39c">
<p local-id=3D"5a7b519abc8f">Push Notifications: Expo Notifications</p></li=
>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"efc86d3e0058" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-PlatformSupport">Platform Support</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"99fdb507-23dc-44d3-9c26-50e57a77b2e4">
<li local-id=3D"90ef97f6-76f5-42bd-a394-b8ee042f6798">
<p local-id=3D"a1ec3f60db4c">iOS: 15.0+ (iPhone 8 and newer)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"088f86b3-4ff5-4de1-8b4b-546d2709c4a7">
<p local-id=3D"309fa34633a3">Android: API 23+ (Android 6.0 Marshmallow and =
newer)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d002d15c-5d05-4e44-b3f6-f68849dc3bb6">
<p local-id=3D"96544548277d">Simultaneous Launch: Both platforms released t=
ogether</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"e5e29176a9af" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-BackendArchitecture">Backend Architecture</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"f097b475bf4d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-APIServerStack">API Server Stack</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3f0fa41c-e3bc-4ec2-a784-2b6405377777">
<li local-id=3D"9c89a999-f718-4afb-ad77-952cc6055abf">
<p local-id=3D"b6b344afdcea">Runtime: Bun (latest - ultra-fast JavaScript r=
untime)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"15061dc9-61d6-4f3a-a184-3fd0c4f104d7">
<p local-id=3D"1d198393c914">Framework: Hono (lightweight, fast HTTP framew=
ork)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6bcea797-3b63-4a42-a846-c43ba1251198">
<p local-id=3D"e45f1a515c54">API Protocol: tRPC 10.x (end-to-end type safet=
y with frontend)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b4be389-4172-4707-8147-bef35645e88b">
<p local-id=3D"468343afddc8">ORM: Drizzle ORM (type-safe, Bun-optimized)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a43f9af-3193-4b70-b542-1750ad13915a">
<p local-id=3D"dd7d24f09ada">Authentication: Better Auth (self-hosted, GDPR=
 compliant)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"79917016-3e93-4b8a-9a97-d2820b20cfe1">
<p local-id=3D"47a78c5a3b61">Real-time: Native WebSockets for live updates<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d75f388-d449-4abb-90b7-c4191280f950">
<p local-id=3D"4559e4bdf141">Validation: Zod (schema validation across stac=
k)</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"f44e13f91feb" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-Database&amp;Storage">Database &amp; Storage</=
h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"3c39cd61e6f7" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-PrimaryDatabase">Primary Database</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ef49cc8c-6d5f-451f-b488-7b712287cfc9">
<li local-id=3D"889fd1ca-819e-48f3-b346-3222d0e07825">
<p local-id=3D"38602824d063">Database: Google Cloud SQL PostgreSQL 16+</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"3e0718ac-1be1-4d26-8f9d-a59b066014bb">
<p local-id=3D"9c122dc95669">Region: EU</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"91a5635c-4061-4d7c-8bc1-48e8441dca0b">
<p local-id=3D"88b7c07357fa">Multi-tenancy: Row-Level Security (RLS) for da=
ta isolation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1ca27116-9d01-4518-8929-7529d5cbcaf7">
<p local-id=3D"38a9941048c3">Backup: Automated daily backups, 30-day retent=
ion</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbb736c4-6c18-403d-8886-e83159eb4afe">
<p local-id=3D"98521ad9ecb3">Encryption: At-rest encryption enabled</p></li=
>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"857f2dcf75bb" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-CachingLayer">Caching Layer</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"4e6868f6-da0c-4ae3-bff1-4922cbaf49bd">
<li local-id=3D"ab6f7aa9-e6b5-497f-8189-aa2507a6ebf4">
<p local-id=3D"a059aaba0eef">Cache: Google Memorystore Redis 7+</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"34230adc-6922-4872-a1a9-47b97a494806">
<p local-id=3D"f1fa81e6e408">Usage: Session storage, frequently accessed da=
ta, rate limiting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af983134-c0f4-4b35-8424-def4ae2a86ef">
<p local-id=3D"935cad7ac281">TTL Strategy: 5 min for dynamic data, 1 hour f=
or semi-static</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"557eeed95726" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-FileStorage">File Storage</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2ffc95d1-2a77-4192-9f89-dc99f06623f1">
<li local-id=3D"1b724842-e2b5-4df3-94e3-24bdffb41f37">
<p local-id=3D"8221014ce5f3">Storage: Google Cloud Storage (GCS)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"54c83e93-e947-4de4-8838-ca40496b8679">
<p local-id=3D"dbe09e68523b">Bucket: EU region, Standard storage class</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"e2801202-8a85-44b8-87c2-bf40680edae7">
<p local-id=3D"9ba3476363b1">Capacity: 100GB free tier for MVP</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f1f7b442-cda1-4f8e-880f-a542cfdabd7f">
<p local-id=3D"cdfcb597d33c">Files: Documents, receipt photos, recipe image=
s, feed photos</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6f59e9aa-895b-4824-bfe8-010d02aba3ac">
<p local-id=3D"89d572a94db6">CDN: Cloud CDN for fast delivery across EU</p>=
</li>
</ul>
