<p local-id=3D"0bae43375414">A2A (Agent-to-Agent): Inter-agent communicatio=
n for complex tasks</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"52b70314a038" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AdminPanel">Admin Panel</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"8e7307db-aebb-4956-953c-4e3ecdbf852b">
<li local-id=3D"74e2066a-19b4-4639-8bb4-677381b14910">
<p local-id=3D"d592f0d90531">Framework: React 18 + TypeScript</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d818446f-83e6-4dea-aeed-ece1911773ac">
<p local-id=3D"d4f24238f244">Admin Library: Refine (CRUD operations, data m=
anagement)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e34a99e1-dfd4-44ef-86e7-489ba4622b9e">
<p local-id=3D"87de0970e781">UI: Ant Design components</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9de5f485-32c3-436d-be83-88d6cf5010db">
<p local-id=3D"6ff2d5c9a953">Charts: Recharts for analytics visualization</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d156b3c3-cdea-4f30-b67b-b25edfce4482">
<p local-id=3D"329f22579f77">Build Tool: Vite (fast dev server and build)</=
p></li>
</ul>
