eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DeploymentArchitecture">Deployment Architectur=
e</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"6b5c68ec-663c-4292-94f2-dad262802299">
<li local-id=3D"526bf560-ad57-4da5-9509-8884b9232991">
<p local-id=3D"b7d026c22efc">Backend: Google Cloud Run (containerized, auto=
-scaling)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4616b1b5-ba40-4cc5-8adb-3db22c9023d5">
<p local-id=3D"908cc095a6bc">Database: Google Cloud SQL (managed PostgreSQL=
)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6a00dd9d-b95b-451e-a760-3d3724b29313">
<p local-id=3D"3a1842410b28">Cache: Google Memorystore (managed Redis)</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"1689a018-d1d7-4cb4-9d13-e52e6fb227f4">
<p local-id=3D"366cc864ba26">Storage: Google Cloud Storage (file hosting)</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"147118fc-5b57-46fb-8111-36ffac49545b">
<p local-id=3D"d91284cf8638">CDN: Cloud CDN (content delivery)</p></li>
