<h2 local-id=3D"ce89d4cca166" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-SecurityArchitecture">Security Architecture</h=
2>
<ul local-id=3D"7239b176-f3cd-4e88-aefa-7fa36f883ac0">
<li local-id=3D"24d2b565-4d1d-4695-a2a3-5d3ac951a365">
<p local-id=3D"d624caf16ae6">Authentication: JWT tokens with refresh token =
rotation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d2d942df-8ab9-4a91-9b87-883ed68d594c">
<p local-id=3D"fe1766344838">API Security: Rate limiting, CORS, input valid=
ation (Zod)</p></li>
