<p local-id=3D"26d6120c60f9">Database Security: Row-Level Security (RLS) fo=
r multi-tenancy</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"878915fc-9f50-4519-b34d-d6ef4f88de9c">
<p local-id=3D"164ea6c3b1c8">File Security: Signed URLs with expiration for=
 GCS access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"473957e7-649c-4a89-8741-3d2d8b7542db">
<p local-id=3D"865f5164bbad">GDPR Compliance: Data residency in EU, encrypt=
ion, audit logs</p></li>
</ul>
<h1 local-id=3D"c8fbe461e9b4" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-9.FreemiumModel&amp;Monetization">9. Freemium =
Model &amp; Monetization</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"6efaa92f333c" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-BusinessModel:FreemiumwithPremiumTier">Busines=
s Model: Freemium with Premium Tier</h2>
<p local-id=3D"3fad94fe7415">The product uses a freemium model to maximize =
user acquisition while monetizing power users who need advanced AI capabili=
ties and unlimited usage.</p>
