<p local-id=3D"901b23dfdc36">All 7 Core Modules: Full access to Calendar, T=
asks, Lists, Expenses, Feed, Documents, Meal Plan</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba8e6f8b-0ca2-4c5e-9109-5705cd3a1046">
<p local-id=3D"9ce85d5e2822">AI Voice Commands: 50 interactions per month</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a1b0ea3b-0456-4cfc-a451-7cd13abdcb2b">
<p local-id=3D"7d3afb760cdd">Storage: 5GB for documents and photos</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3b04a392-151b-48b3-ae4c-04c30e4f22ce">
<p local-id=3D"ff78adbf0816">Notifications: All notifications included</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"0bacc74b-cef5-42b3-b915-0d6c79ec44e2">
<p local-id=3D"35773ba6451c">Offline Access: Calendar and Lists work offlin=
e</p></li>
</ul>
