<h2 local-id=3D"871322444781" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-PricingStrategyRationale">Pricing Strategy Rat=
ionale</h2>
<p local-id=3D"41ea49d812f3">Pricing is positioned competitively against pr=
oductivity tools (Todoist Premium at =E2=82=AC5/month) and family apps (Coz=
i Premium at $4.99/month), but higher to reflect the AI-powered capabilitie=
s and all-in-one value proposition.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d2bbde92f8e5">=E2=82=AC9.99/month is the sweet spot for Euro=
pean consumers for productivity software. The annual plan (=E2=82=AC99.99/y=
ear) offers 17% savings to encourage commitment and reduce churn.</p>
