<h1 local-id=3D"1a228f593a71" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-10.SuccessMetrics&amp;KPIs">10. Success Metric=
s &amp; KPIs</h1>
<p local-id=3D"70ae28506c43">Success for MVP is measured across three dimen=
sions: User Engagement, Feature Adoption, and Revenue. These KPIs will be t=
racked daily via analytics dashboard.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"3a5728702127" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-PrimaryKPIs(MustTrackfromDay1)">Primary KPIs (=
Must Track from Day 1)</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"32f2a75c13ea" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-1.DailyActiveUsers(DAU)">1. Daily Active Users=
 (DAU)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3f52f318-a1f6-413b-a8dc-027da57e2ec1">
<li local-id=3D"dc5a7892-8303-40e6-a7ff-f7462eb88e14">
<p local-id=3D"aac056931328">Definition: Unique users who open the app and =
perform at least one action per day</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b1add27-38a7-466d-929b-c096f0786c64">
<p local-id=3D"27288571cef0">Target: 60% of registered users (Week 1) =E2=
=86=92 40% stabilized (Month 3)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c4424a4-c761-4644-8c21-96f22b670fdf">
<p local-id=3D"f93086b9c417">Measurement: Firebase Analytics / Mixpanel</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"8cf4f930-f43f-4406-98f1-4171dad4e0f7">
<p local-id=3D"ff9c2f1becc6">Why Important: Core engagement metric; shows p=
roduct stickiness</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"4b6eaec8b326" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-2.FeatureEngagementRate">2. Feature Engagement=
 Rate</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"28a1b216-881f-4a54-a9cd-5d6f69cfbcd0">
<li local-id=3D"ecc30d8f-5c91-4f01-8758-17bbfb807a53">
<p local-id=3D"56cb38d8a411">Definition: % of weekly active users who inter=
act with 3+ modules per week</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de9e8285-cd2c-4f86-bfb4-3f3b57d5e0f8">
<p local-id=3D"8683fda0ad2b">Target: 60%+ (users using at least 3 of 7 modu=
les weekly)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"41919b2b-65b0-46c1-afa5-c7f8e200b168">
<p local-id=3D"6ba86e2246c8">Measurement: Custom event tracking per module<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"39f89255-28d3-4778-b2ce-bcf614cca489">
<p local-id=3D"ccd6ca72a405">Why Important: Validates all-in-one value prop=
osition; higher engagement =3D higher retention</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"4ced6ddbdc05" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-SecondaryKPIs(MonitorWeekly)">Secondary KPIs (=
Monitor Weekly)</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"1e175d8f3e4e" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-3.VoiceCommandAdoptionRate">3. Voice Command A=
doption Rate</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2219af8d-e5e9-48b8-85b5-f9aa50ba185a">
<li local-id=3D"04577595-3c5d-413b-a2d8-6d14c6e0d011">
<p local-id=3D"f85679bcfea0">Definition: % of interactions performed via vo=
ice vs manual input</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1255d432-3045-4229-86fc-a4750745a637">
<p local-id=3D"faedddfd5132">Target: 40%+ within first 2 weeks of user onbo=
arding</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8aa0f994-190f-4dd7-8ce6-47176fdb941e">
<p local-id=3D"a14b3dc1f14f">Why Important: Key differentiator; validates v=
oice-first hypothesis</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"c8ae98881f44" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-4.WeeklyActiveUsers(WAU)">4. Weekly Active Use=
rs (WAU)</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"1ac22fa1-85d0-4a6c-9bcc-13f2bace553f">
<li local-id=3D"68f616a8-67a0-4405-8295-8ea9854c1993">
<p local-id=3D"5f40ba91bc75">Target: 75%+ of registered users</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d433223-149d-4bad-be3d-e173a716e620">
<p local-id=3D"704dbef84fff">Why Important: Broader engagement indicator th=
an DAU</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8ebf8578905d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-5.UserRetention">5. User Retention</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"701a9594-5533-47b5-8934-623b73e50a99">
<li local-id=3D"3d2afebb-5776-4c0b-a026-12dac1493a2c">
<p local-id=3D"6ef02cf1413a">Day 1 Retention: 70%+ (users who return next d=
ay)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"766a30d5-7c62-4b8c-86b4-c25526be4523">
<p local-id=3D"49853956b212">Day 7 Retention: 50%+ (users still active afte=
r 1 week)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"14a99262-735a-40e1-ae9d-92979761d78c">
<p local-id=3D"c894d42cb344">Day 30 Retention: 30%+ (users still active aft=
er 1 month)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"411caf6a-8c4d-40dd-a201-d345ca3f4c73">
<p local-id=3D"94deb97c0a36">Why Important: Indicates product-market fit an=
d long-term viability</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"6e7338a169ce" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-6.PremiumConversionRate">6. Premium Conversion=
 Rate</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3d9edaf9-3d6a-481f-ac4f-6d94477b248a">
<li local-id=3D"acdb3f0b-6b03-47d5-8f31-ce0345ebb3a9">
<p local-id=3D"16cb2babb170">Target: 5-8% of free users convert to Premium =
within 30 days</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22260493-51b4-4a86-9032-ccb298e9e676">
<p local-id=3D"d50440d8f4f8">Why Important: Revenue sustainability and mone=
tization validation</p></li>
</ul>
