<h2 local-id=3D"feb705451b57" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-SuccessCriteriaforMVPLaunch">Success Criteria =
for MVP Launch</h2>
<p local-id=3D"aeb9d7be6b71">MVP is considered successful if, after 90 days=
:</p>
<ol start=3D"6" local-id=3D"02828850-b454-4b23-99f6-0669857ae06a">
<li local-id=3D"beeab22b-caec-4513-99f8-4139e66ebd1e">
<p local-id=3D"22f6878d862b">1,000+ daily active users</p></li>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"59a0246c-3c21-4636-890b-920e5554afda">
<li local-id=3D"3ade467c-2ddd-48fd-8a34-4ab05e3e3a11">
<p local-id=3D"ba743c8da793">60%+ feature engagement rate (3+ modules weekl=
y)</p></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"7" local-id=3D"f8c8c01a-45ce-490b-a9f7-117eec2d94d0">
<li local-id=3D"7ba94e10-4f5d-46fd-a68d-f69d10d88eee">
<p local-id=3D"810acb537094">40%+ voice command adoption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5b8e889-39a2-4ab5-8c7a-0c607291c114">
<p local-id=3D"09f72ad87064">5%+ premium conversion rate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22b800c0-c4aa-48aa-a804-2bed29b3fa81">
<p local-id=3D"943e38d55dd3">30%+ Day 30 retention</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a8f9db76-a940-4be4-bb62-ed89d56797bf">
<p local-id=3D"bc7dd7637c08">4.0+ App Store rating (both iOS and Android)</=
p></li>
</ol>
<h2 local-id=3D"576c85b8f0e5" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-AnalyticsStack">Analytics Stack</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"928f7825-df4d-4371-a1bc-ba670ee3a391">
<li local-id=3D"60eb9242-a40e-44b2-a421-ac0e25cf0cd0">
<p local-id=3D"74b9ee89b29a">Firebase Analytics: User events, session track=
ing</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"478bdcb5-906e-4be7-92bb-a6db008d5467">
<p local-id=3D"7d7389bfc8a0">Mixpanel: Advanced funnel analysis, cohort ana=
lysis</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4661eca2-0a5b-4eb4-a086-604855fd874e">
<p local-id=3D"565a3eaa82f2">PostHog: Session replay, feature flags, A/B te=
sting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f1de3087-7fde-4837-af12-7ffb60f01c88">
<p local-id=3D"b0d63dbaa476">Custom Dashboard: Real-time KPI monitoring (Re=
charts + React)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"42537a5e252b"></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"33e532f11124" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-11.GDPR&amp;DataPrivacy">11. GDPR &amp; Data P=
rivacy</h1>
<p local-id=3D"a0e17ece9744">As a product launching in the European Union, =
GDPR compliance is not optional. The Family OS is designed with privacy-by-=
design principles and gives users full control over their data.</p>
<h2 local-id=3D"6e4c34484581" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-GDPRComplianceRequirements">GDPR Compliance Re=
quirements</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"28290c7afbfe" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataResidency">Data Residency</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"c06558d8-f79a-4e70-98af-881d9999e2c9">
<li local-id=3D"b6e1fe25-2f0d-43f3-a0e4-5f8c5576fce4">
<p local-id=3D"7e355d0d56cf">All user data stored in EU region (Google Clou=
d Frankfurt or Belgium)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5ec8e5a5-8a0c-4254-98bc-66df03a04c00">
<p local-id=3D"0ba2d432a215">No data transfer outside EU without explicit c=
onsent</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a857d894-77f6-4568-baa5-2cd72ac2bd09">
<p local-id=3D"20c7ef43e079">AI processing: Gemini API calls routed through=
 EU endpoints</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"69419da5d1be" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-UserRights">User Rights</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"a4e82efe-f2b3-4e72-a90d-2f384ead442e">
<li local-id=3D"dd0f9c0e-fc20-430a-a24c-c0063c581d8d">
<p local-id=3D"515a93d1a48a">Right to Access: Users can download all their =
data anytime (JSON export)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"642112cf-7340-4ee5-a25f-7708235eadc5">
<p local-id=3D"436f506a85c9">Right to Rectification: Users can edit all dat=
a through app</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a791387-ba25-4c21-8516-5ca744adce7c">
<p local-id=3D"6d0190718ccc">Right to Erasure: Account deletion removes all=
 data within 30 days</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e0a63226-5eab-4a3d-a185-b5508e17ab83">
<p local-id=3D"3d2555bdafec">Right to Data Portability: Export to CSV/JSON =
format</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"33711a2d-3eae-4290-a266-658f2d1f9d9d">
<p local-id=3D"f23245c04f07">Right to Object: Users can disable AI processi=
ng of their data</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"516b1618b83d" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-ConsentManagement">Consent Management</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ce2a3dc8-ad71-48ad-96f5-ccdf2346ad8c">
<li local-id=3D"b4ab3cd2-66f3-4708-878b-40fa549e796c">
<p local-id=3D"593a2700cadb">Explicit Consent: Clear opt-in for data proces=
sing, AI features, analytics</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0a2bd15c-0547-4ad0-8ede-49d4866e9f88">
<p local-id=3D"826507143a8c">Granular Controls: Separate toggles for differ=
ent data uses</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"468b93cd-dc5c-4d53-a0b1-b5627097d9c8">
<p local-id=3D"96541f18b365">Cookie Consent: GDPR-compliant cookie banner (=
if web version launched)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"daccc18e-dbe6-4bc0-b3a2-91e7d2715255">
<p local-id=3D"cdf30caba0ac">Child Data: Extra safeguards for users under 1=
8</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"cc57ce1cd05b" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataMinimization">Data Minimization</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"268f3555-c1a1-423e-85f7-0e5fea1b4475">
<li local-id=3D"2053e8ff-f38b-444d-bd55-e86b853582f1">
<p local-id=3D"98f1829c0282">Only collect data necessary for app functional=
ity</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4b42ca3-b36f-43d0-b9e5-d1e6c5e60f70">
<p local-id=3D"1233fe46f878">No third-party tracking pixels or analytics SD=
Ks that share PII</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c70d7e5-27b9-4522-9788-8429439cf40d">
<p local-id=3D"ff11c99fae87">Voice recordings: Processed locally on device,=
 not stored in cloud</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83c79fcb-9813-4beb-b8c0-96ee7c61e375">
<p local-id=3D"e9bc4357947f">Photos: Stored encrypted, only accessible by f=
amily members</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"800ca5b7ae45" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-SecurityMeasures">Security Measures</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"a7b4d36d-cdf5-4926-bc70-cdf4175704b6">
<li local-id=3D"2fc3692c-dd91-4cae-a5ec-c3f48e380bd6">
<p local-id=3D"fbbba43071e0">Encryption: AES-256 at rest, TLS 1.3 in transi=
t</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5fb61583-2a92-469c-8ff3-534fb794c1e8">
<p local-id=3D"c8f6d0359fd2">Access Control: Role-based permissions, audit =
logs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a610f6c6-a84d-4841-8830-8abfd3788ae3">
<p local-id=3D"844be6335510">Authentication: Secure JWT with refresh tokens=
, optional 2FA</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d763ef50-7503-494b-babd-28a1c3df9a43">
<p local-id=3D"70ed6ab7932d">Data Isolation: Row-Level Security (RLS) in Po=
stgreSQL</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbe105f3-2af6-4ed2-85e5-b37ed6486cf5">
<p local-id=3D"4a5e38d8726e">Breach Notification: 72-hour notification prot=
ocol if data breach occurs</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"aa6864d56bbc" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-PrivacyPolicy&amp;Terms">Privacy Policy &amp; =
Terms</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"a0ade398-4c38-4a68-a37b-a37533035b10">
<li local-id=3D"e1267270-56a8-4aac-b7dc-5900647a9f54">
<p local-id=3D"85ffa2ac5dc8">Clear, Plain Language: Avoid legal jargon, exp=
lain in simple terms</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3dcc7ead-31e9-40b0-beb8-c09c63fc9733">
<p local-id=3D"9b773ae64045">Updated for GDPR: Cover all user rights and da=
ta practices</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1895af95-5a94-4876-96e4-5d10c464eebb">
<p local-id=3D"dd5c67b3e8c3">Accessible: Always available in-app, displayed=
 during onboarding</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba0e36be-519a-4e72-bc4a-3af8434b8baa">
<p local-id=3D"3833386356d8">Multi-language: Privacy policy in English, Ger=
man, French, Spanish</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"3c9d33c673d5" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-DataProcessingRegister">Data Processing Regist=
er</h2>
<p local-id=3D"a9f22b59348f">Maintain internal register of data processing =
activities:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b5eef670-43bc-43b6-8430-5122a42fe422">
<li local-id=3D"266dfcd0-c6f7-4703-91b0-a8b8c9c11105">
<p local-id=3D"00cef458dfd7">What data is collected (name, email, family da=
ta, AI interactions)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6cc8f759-9c98-4156-a485-ce64d53babbe">
<p local-id=3D"8d9cbac05bfb">Why it is collected (app functionality, AI fea=
tures)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f843480-57c3-4f1a-8ac0-701a6ddcf5ae">
<p local-id=3D"62cea883e94d">How long it is stored (active accounts: indefi=
nite; deleted accounts: 30 days)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7cfa7eb3-7cc7-41e1-a597-7848e14b66a4">
<p local-id=3D"efdcd0788478">Who has access (family members, admin support =
with user consent)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5fe5d700-c032-4f84-a685-324259a9e890">
<p local-id=3D"d176cc2912e9">Third parties involved (Google Cloud, Gemini A=
I - all GDPR compliant)</p></li>
</ul>
<h2 local-id=3D"47c92f5be472" id=3D"ProductRequirementsDocument(PRD)-AI-Pow=
eredFamilyManagementPlatform-ChildPrivacy(Under16)">Child Privacy (Under 16=
)</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"47988242-4b09-4080-ae15-d2f75f49dfd1">
<li local-id=3D"8c945411-9965-427e-ac70-993e56a3bcc0">
<p local-id=3D"8872fe77d7e8">Parental Consent Required: Parents must approv=
e child account creation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"619e6dda-8b11-48fc-b116-125d547d105f">
<p local-id=3D"713692261ed5">Limited Data Collection: No behavioral trackin=
g for children</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fd520255-fc93-4e2e-b1e3-92dfdb698d26">
<p local-id=3D"b1f81c96520b">No Third-Party Sharing: Child data never share=
d with advertisers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"46603bd0-a923-461c-a3c8-39424b7fbfc4">
<p local-id=3D"24c9381e18fe">Educational Transparency: Explain to children =
(age-appropriate) how their data is used</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ba9733f3f531"></p>
